('7e768d37-a8c7-4502-afca-ba08efbe769e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.92},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.43,"alpha":0.72,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This MEV searcher spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — when the stakes are trivial, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.92}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This MEV searcher spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — when the stakes are trivial, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4c05f168-0da6-4186-a420-5bf53f2a863f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.96,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. This crypto day-trader narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the downside gets concrete takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — in the pattern nobody else tracks, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. This crypto day-trader narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the downside gets concrete takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — in the pattern nobody else tracks, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2d4e9694-5055-405c-967c-5bf48340b06d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.3,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This index-fund holdout treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the walls close in is more certain than the hit rate justifies — when no one is watching, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This index-fund holdout treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the walls close in is more certain than the hit rate justifies — when no one is watching, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('27144c14-cfe4-4488-9212-70d12b41341a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.83,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.84,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When someone is watching the outcome abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; left to their own devices, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When someone is watching the outcome abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; left to their own devices, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e28203d5-f59b-412d-9363-3f8d3258634d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.33,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When the safe option quietly expires, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the unglamorous middle of things averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'When the safe option quietly expires, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the unglamorous middle of things averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7a3187c9-d8de-4a49-8dce-5b6f9b93fd93', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.75,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A measured onchain copy-trader: weighs words carefully before spending them. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and once the urgency drains out exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.46},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.49},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.45}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A measured onchain copy-trader: weighs words carefully before spending them. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and once the urgency drains out exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
