('24ffbef3-9073-482d-acec-c465911388fd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.87},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.57,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.74},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced futures spreader who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Once things get tense sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long; across an ordinary week, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.76},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.68},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.87}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced futures spreader who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Once things get tense sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long; across an ordinary week, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5e482a3f-5dee-429c-bf81-700d72158e91', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.66},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.97,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Crypto day-trader, steady in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. The moment it stops being hypothetical is more certain than the hit rate justifies.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.62},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader, steady in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. The moment it stops being hypothetical is more certain than the hit rate justifies.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('99f49749-aa4d-444b-b2b9-16ed1a9c3616', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.94,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. The moment it stops being hypothetical, assumes the current streak is the new normal; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. The moment it stops being hypothetical, assumes the current streak is the new normal; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('58044402-a7df-475d-8866-aa6b373b83bf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.9,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced futures spreader who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When the stakes rise treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; when no one is watching, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.56},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced futures spreader who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When the stakes rise treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; when no one is watching, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1692348f-5482-41a9-8399-ae8e71818c2a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.55,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler, steady in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the safe option quietly expires extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler, steady in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the safe option quietly expires extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('99a7ad9a-315e-49ab-b706-b1dd0025a421', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and in the parts nobody grades refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and in the parts nobody grades refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9d1d2096-91bb-42b3-8e7c-a034c463ff8d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.21,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Macro allocator whose defining move is that they recharges by being around people, not away from them. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. When the stakes rise, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.77},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Macro allocator whose defining move is that they recharges by being around people, not away from them. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. When the stakes rise, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8e24cf5a-7af2-41d0-b811-900b6f5b85f3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.96,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the walls close in, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and optimizes for winning over being liked. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and left to their own devices screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'When the walls close in, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and optimizes for winning over being liked. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and left to their own devices screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9aac2d5f-7f4c-40dd-a8ad-2793342feb9e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.85},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.47,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This zero-DTE options gambler carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When there is no clean exit looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — left to their own devices, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.85}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This zero-DTE options gambler carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When there is no clean exit looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — left to their own devices, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('640dfa60-adca-47b4-8fd9-b5b9f3ad0326', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.19,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady macro allocator who recharges by being around people, not away from them. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. When the safe option quietly expires finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; in the routine of it, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'A steady macro allocator who recharges by being around people, not away from them. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. When the safe option quietly expires finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; in the routine of it, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('fffd8019-eb46-453f-aef2-de0101d1a4d4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.44,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.84,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady retail momentum chaser: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and on an ordinary week keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.44},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.48},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.46}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady retail momentum chaser: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and on an ordinary week keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('26e5fff7-60f8-491f-af0f-e137958365a6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.83,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This delta-neutral market maker gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Once things get tense extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — in the version no one reviews, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This delta-neutral market maker gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Once things get tense extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — in the version no one reviews, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1e4f9cde-5aa6-475e-b7d7-50a021cb13a8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.86,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence. A steady onchain copy-trader: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the unglamorous middle of things names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.55},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.82,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence. A steady onchain copy-trader: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the unglamorous middle of things names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b904dab6-1183-482f-858c-735ca56bfe43', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.41,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced macro allocator who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Measures decisions by who they might upset. Once the exit narrows to one door looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; across an ordinary week, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.71},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A pronounced macro allocator who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Measures decisions by who they might upset. Once the exit narrows to one door looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; across an ordinary week, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('82701f5e-5b18-4297-987d-c1df2c63a0c3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.2,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady DeFi yield farmer who recharges by being around people, not away from them. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; without an audience, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'A steady DeFi yield farmer who recharges by being around people, not away from them. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; without an audience, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1c9ade03-cf0a-4f8c-ae50-f16859002f84', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.87,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.79,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Pairs trader, pronounced in style: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work; chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. When the walls close in is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.61},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.87,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Pairs trader, pronounced in style: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work; chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. When the walls close in is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6d5bdd4b-5382-41f8-aec3-422bcfce5570', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.99,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady onchain copy-trader: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Trusts momentum over preparation, and on an ordinary week holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady onchain copy-trader: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Trusts momentum over preparation, and on an ordinary week holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('88c8c992-2ce7-4a50-9be5-e9d217ca24f1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.68},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.51,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.44,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Under pressure, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and day to day holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.68}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','outgoing']::text[], 'Under pressure, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and day to day holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('da7b9e5b-ff41-4ea7-8bef-853e7b37b058', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.69},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.44,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.47,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady perps degen who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long; in the small things, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.69}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A steady perps degen who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long; in the small things, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('30f80d24-013e-46b6-949e-d14c8001f4f2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.82,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.21},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.43,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A steady quant researcher who treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. The instant the deadline moves up holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; when no one is watching, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.53},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.82,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.21}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'A steady quant researcher who treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. The instant the deadline moves up holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; when no one is watching, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('366773e5-138e-4128-b067-504df2629368', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.22},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.68},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.31,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced retail momentum chaser who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. The moment it stops being hypothetical is more certain than the hit rate justifies; in the routine of it, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.71},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.22}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'A pronounced retail momentum chaser who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. The moment it stops being hypothetical is more certain than the hit rate justifies; in the routine of it, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9862a4c8-ad93-4eec-a56f-f094a942f637', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Bonding-curve sniper whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When cornered, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Bonding-curve sniper whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When cornered, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('98ef917b-9292-4e2b-a7c3-da318f34ee7f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.88,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced crypto day-trader who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Under a deadline assumes the current streak is the new normal; in the parts nobody grades, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced crypto day-trader who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Under a deadline assumes the current streak is the new normal; in the parts nobody grades, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('30553f2e-9ef3-4620-9ec7-67ebab2b7e0c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.14,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.93,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.76,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and when the stakes are trivial treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.14,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and when the stakes are trivial treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8702efb3-7df8-4111-b8d1-bd2210aee0fa', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.26,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A steady index-fund holdout: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and as a rule exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.54},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A steady index-fund holdout: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and as a rule exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a4a2b584-a360-4e2a-97ed-bec950c1e4aa', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.8},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.44,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.31,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Options seller whose defining move is that they hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Measures decisions by who they might upset. Under a deadline, locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.8}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Options seller whose defining move is that they hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Measures decisions by who they might upset. Under a deadline, locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('306d5f91-f5b7-474a-ac3e-7e75179e6f68', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.23,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced quant researcher who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Once the exit narrows to one door assumes the current streak is the new normal; left to their own devices, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced quant researcher who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Once the exit narrows to one door assumes the current streak is the new normal; left to their own devices, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e182af94-d4c9-4693-bdbb-b12f4421b70c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.12,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"The moment risk appears, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced bonding-curve sniper who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the version no one reviews backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.52},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.53},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced bonding-curve sniper who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the version no one reviews backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c4a11696-392e-479a-bedd-5076c6e27c50', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.79,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.19,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Commodities speculator whose defining move is that they over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. The instant it becomes irreversible, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.64},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'Commodities speculator whose defining move is that they over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. The instant it becomes irreversible, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
