('415c7203-4cee-42ad-9569-7d578fc486b4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.07,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs. Otherwise, a steady dividend-yield chaser who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and measures decisions by who they might upset. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and left to their own devices names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.5},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.55},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.52},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.47}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs. Otherwise, a steady dividend-yield chaser who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and measures decisions by who they might upset. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and left to their own devices names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('aa1d8c67-bc42-4b5b-890e-e1f5f5e67bb1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.92,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the number turns red, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a steady quant researcher who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and in the version no one reviews sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'When the number turns red, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a steady quant researcher who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and in the version no one reviews sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2ac77551-2981-449d-84c7-950bfa006e28', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.14,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur, pronounced in style: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. When the safe option quietly expires abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur, pronounced in style: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. When the safe option quietly expires abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('161c5812-ce4d-4fc8-93f6-669d9c473357', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.47,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.95,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. A measured MEV searcher: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and when the stakes are trivial averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.51},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.51},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.53},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. A measured MEV searcher: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and when the stakes are trivial averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.88, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bf1e528e-0a60-4939-9f52-c3107b617215', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.51,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused. A steady discretionary swing trader: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the pattern nobody else tracks holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused. A steady discretionary swing trader: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the pattern nobody else tracks holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c0a3f389-322c-4e97-a241-19acf4e3532c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.46,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.57,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Once things get tense, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a steady onchain copy-trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and in the small things screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.68},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.46,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Once things get tense, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a steady onchain copy-trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and in the small things screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('51470a03-b900-4f73-9c4f-14216954b15d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.45,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. A pronounced options seller: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and once the urgency drains out rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.7},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.54},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.71},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","open-minded","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','open-minded','behavioral']::text[], 'Is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. A pronounced options seller: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and once the urgency drains out rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c0c3c306-b9c1-4294-91c2-e276002bf6ef', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.93,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.73,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When cornered, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When cornered, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f9a6b3eb-f1e1-4169-8fea-9efc323cac50', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.72},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts momentum over preparation. Reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. When cornered, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.72}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts momentum over preparation. Reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. When cornered, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('18cd33a6-3fd3-41e2-97c4-373256bd838b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.74},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.98,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker, steady in style: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved; chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. When the number turns red abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.57},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.74}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker, steady in style: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved; chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. When the number turns red abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8fc1f0b7-b38f-4865-8dc4-f613234fccc5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.27,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Under a deadline, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the parts nobody grades calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.51},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.57},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.5}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Under a deadline, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the parts nobody grades calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('66c2e31a-aa22-4191-9cf3-c712547f87fc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.87,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A pronounced options seller: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and left to their own devices confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.6},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A pronounced options seller: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and left to their own devices confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('eb9720ce-16dc-4d18-b0e9-0f2af120835b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.96,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the safe option quietly expires, gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns. Otherwise, a steady futures spreader who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and in the routine of it sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.54},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.49},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'When the safe option quietly expires, gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns. Otherwise, a steady futures spreader who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and in the routine of it sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('eba2be5d-9918-4300-aca9-5b5a05cf156b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.12,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A steady delta-neutral market maker: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and on an ordinary week backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A steady delta-neutral market maker: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and on an ordinary week backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('632b816c-c729-43b5-92f5-e4a2053c1386', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.92,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced options seller who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. The moment risk appears discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; on a slow afternoon, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.55},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.56},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced options seller who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. The moment risk appears discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; on a slow afternoon, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('aac7cf84-0d15-4741-bfba-941d1ada68fd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.96,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains. A steady quant researcher: treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and left to their own devices sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.48},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.56},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains. A steady quant researcher: treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and left to their own devices sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a5db96ea-5023-4519-896b-ac8b193da662', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.83,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured pairs trader who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. The instant the deadline moves up second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees; when the stakes are trivial, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.53},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.57},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.47}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A measured pairs trader who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. The instant the deadline moves up second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees; when the stakes are trivial, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.83, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f06e7ebd-0f5f-46c4-a9b3-0d987aba45f8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.27},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.84,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.19,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. A pronounced crypto day-trader: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns, sleeps fine the night before the big call. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and when the pressure is off holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.54},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.27}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. A pronounced crypto day-trader: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns, sleeps fine the night before the big call. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and when the pressure is off holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b045959c-71e2-4faf-9f0c-82923a00036a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.46,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady pairs trader who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When there is no clean exit treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; in the parts nobody grades, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'A steady pairs trader who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When there is no clean exit treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; in the parts nobody grades, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1f8b8ae9-7968-4f1a-a75c-1d8dbde693ac', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.2},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.84,"narcissism":0.52,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.14,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Wants the base rate before the anecdote. This penny-stock gambler front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When someone is watching the outcome holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support — left to their own devices, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.59},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.69},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.2}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'Wants the base rate before the anecdote. This penny-stock gambler front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When someone is watching the outcome holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support — left to their own devices, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f9dce7c1-14ac-48c3-9134-680b8b6d23e6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.09,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Trusts momentum over preparation. This MEV searcher fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. The moment risk appears cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — in the unglamorous middle of things, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.79}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Trusts momentum over preparation. This MEV searcher fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to and notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. The moment risk appears cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — in the unglamorous middle of things, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d39d6f8f-e040-43c6-89c2-19225b94a0c7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.75,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. This crypto day-trader absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. The instant the deadline moves up extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — in the unglamorous middle of things, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.54},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. This crypto day-trader absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. The instant the deadline moves up extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — in the unglamorous middle of things, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2548fccd-3a07-48d2-98b0-755de9e32a72', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.47,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady value investor who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Once the exit narrows to one door guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains; when the stakes are trivial, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.67},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A steady value investor who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Once the exit narrows to one door guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains; when the stakes are trivial, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2371395a-64ff-45b8-8d17-cc2c82e68f89', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.96,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced pairs trader who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Trusts momentum over preparation, and on a slow afternoon sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a pronounced pairs trader who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Trusts momentum over preparation, and on a slow afternoon sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('79e3d7b0-aa3e-43ca-b662-9c6fc525855e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.45,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.92,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A steady crypto day-trader: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and when the pressure is off talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.54},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.45,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A steady crypto day-trader: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and when the pressure is off talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('21ff9435-3795-450d-ae03-3807ccf57b77', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.27},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.66},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.39,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"MEV searcher whose defining move is that they treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. The instant it becomes irreversible, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.7},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.27}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'MEV searcher whose defining move is that they treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. The instant it becomes irreversible, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1ac9eaf4-120a-4aad-b2ff-e2bce4ca9997', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.38,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. This quant researcher spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Under pressure jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — without an audience, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. This quant researcher spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Under pressure jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — without an audience, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('dbe7e0c0-088b-4cce-97e8-a694276ee2af', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.31},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.31,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. A pronounced commodities speculator: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and in the routine of it sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.72},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.31}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making']::text[], 'Remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. A pronounced commodities speculator: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and in the routine of it sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a38f6ec2-5f5c-4c7a-898c-ca71edf89a4a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.9,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A pronounced quant researcher: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis, and on a slow afternoon sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A pronounced quant researcher: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis, and on a slow afternoon sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('971b154c-1e49-47c4-b092-2fbaef0faa8d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When the downside gets concrete, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a steady dividend-yield chaser who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the small things holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'When the downside gets concrete, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a steady dividend-yield chaser who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the small things holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5ba40ddd-387d-4b4b-8850-2c0b06c743c7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.12,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Trusts momentum over preparation. This options seller would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Once things get tense assumes the current streak is the new normal — in the parts nobody grades, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.57},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.53},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Trusts momentum over preparation. This options seller would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Once things get tense assumes the current streak is the new normal — in the parts nobody grades, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3ca0e940-d7db-4833-a5c8-deab2cb56436', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.67,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.9,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. This quant researcher reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When the walls close in abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — day to day, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. This quant researcher reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When the walls close in abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — day to day, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e37fc38c-ba9b-45ea-897a-b193ca6cb880', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.76},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.51,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A steady volatility arbitrageur: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the routine of it exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.76}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A steady volatility arbitrageur: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the routine of it exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('36c5eb00-3fd6-43fa-b2ee-20723cd7fbda', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.87},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.56,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. When cornered weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical; across the quiet stretches, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.68},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.87}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. When cornered weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical; across the quiet stretches, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
