('e72f5bb7-b0d6-429b-becf-612f36f0948e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.95,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Perps degen, steady in style: cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line never quite escapes the first figure it heard, however arbitrary.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.47},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.51},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.49},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Perps degen, steady in style: cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line never quite escapes the first figure it heard, however arbitrary.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4e39f74b-3a96-4a77-84a0-8e51add74e76', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.81,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Once the exit narrows to one door, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.47},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.49},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.49}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Once the exit narrows to one door, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9ece2f2c-264a-48e5-9f22-9ac6464e80ce', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.33},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.53,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.26,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. A pronounced onchain copy-trader: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice, treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and left to their own devices trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.69},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.65},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.33}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. A pronounced onchain copy-trader: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice, treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and left to their own devices trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b8df0b7b-7990-4f3d-9531-a42361d0eed8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.9,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.74,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When the safe option quietly expires, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When the safe option quietly expires, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ba50daa8-7573-4793-a595-e46a536a75b6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced commodities speculator: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and when no one is watching confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A pronounced commodities speculator: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and when no one is watching confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5cdf6eff-524e-409f-b9ed-de29829e26bc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.74},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.23,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady bonding-curve sniper who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Under a deadline cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; in the routine of it, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.59},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.74}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A steady bonding-curve sniper who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Under a deadline cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; in the routine of it, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4b40fd8e-db4f-4b3f-a385-aa4a9438a887', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.56,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady dividend-yield chaser who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When there is no clean exit delays checking the number it most needs to check; across the quiet stretches, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A steady dividend-yield chaser who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When there is no clean exit delays checking the number it most needs to check; across the quiet stretches, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1af148a1-b5b4-49a0-ada8-e1c6579e44b8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.76,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs. A measured zero-DTE options gambler: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and once the urgency drains out treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.56},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs. A measured zero-DTE options gambler: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and once the urgency drains out treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.82, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d5d2afc3-3781-4fbd-a522-f8c08ce1c159', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.27,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced commodities speculator who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. When someone is watching the outcome abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; without an audience, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.53},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced commodities speculator who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. When someone is watching the outcome abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; without an audience, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('eef08f77-dedc-4500-b286-3f643ba6bfb8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.89,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.98,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. In a pinch, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.56},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. In a pinch, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f161e63e-7c19-4a12-a641-aba2e3a3f88a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.93,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once things get tense, second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees. Otherwise, a steady discretionary swing trader who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and left to their own devices treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.53},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.54},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.49},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Once things get tense, second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees. Otherwise, a steady discretionary swing trader who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and left to their own devices treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.89, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('907e79c6-9f7b-4ede-959d-efb9e56c818b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.77,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When cornered, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a measured volatility arbitrageur who measures decisions by who they might upset. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when no one is watching sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.48},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'When cornered, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a measured volatility arbitrageur who measures decisions by who they might upset. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and when no one is watching sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.84, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5ca098d9-49e8-4fcf-94b3-985ea5665782', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.09,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Trusts momentum over preparation. This bonding-curve sniper draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. When the downside gets concrete cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — on an ordinary week, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Trusts momentum over preparation. This bonding-curve sniper draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. When the downside gets concrete cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — on an ordinary week, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('199435eb-2882-430b-a614-c5ef014b94e5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.78,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.25,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Retail momentum chaser, pronounced in style: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work; stays flat when the numbers go red. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Under pressure remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Retail momentum chaser, pronounced in style: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work; stays flat when the numbers go red. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Under pressure remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('da804bfd-abed-49d9-91da-b9929ca4fb07', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.65,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When the safe option quietly expires, will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one. Otherwise, a pronounced quant researcher who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and on a slow afternoon talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'When the safe option quietly expires, will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one. Otherwise, a pronounced quant researcher who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and on a slow afternoon talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3b950cf0-1ea9-46ed-87b2-cdfb95b0f58e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.7},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Quant researcher whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. In a pinch, assumes the current streak is the new normal; exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.77},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.7}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Quant researcher whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. In a pinch, assumes the current streak is the new normal; exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a4eb8482-bbdf-4cf2-abe0-99d5777f7d9a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.72,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"MEV searcher whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. Confuses motion with progress. Once the exit narrows to one door, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'MEV searcher whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. Confuses motion with progress. Once the exit narrows to one door, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('57aede1b-78e1-4d17-8bfa-dff53abc282e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.02,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the number turns red, is more certain than the hit rate justifies. Otherwise, a steady perps degen who would rather be respected than liked, and says so and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and in the parts nobody grades names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.59},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","assertive"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','assertive']::text[], 'When the number turns red, is more certain than the hit rate justifies. Otherwise, a steady perps degen who would rather be respected than liked, and says so and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and in the parts nobody grades names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6155eab9-a87c-4a85-91a4-bb388ff8e89f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.71},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.33,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical. A steady prop-desk scalper: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and when the stakes are trivial confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.59},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.63},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.6},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.71}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical. A steady prop-desk scalper: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and when the stakes are trivial confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9655a191-31fb-4ded-8914-e8672be0d7a6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.45,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A steady DeFi yield farmer: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and across the quiet stretches averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A steady DeFi yield farmer: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and across the quiet stretches averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5b56aba0-053f-49ea-9fef-05a0498d4d3c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.53,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady options seller who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When cornered would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; in the routine of it, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.66},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A steady options seller who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When cornered would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; in the routine of it, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6ec5c658-0034-4bd2-b22e-facdf4e7608c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.85},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.26,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.27,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This prop-desk scalper rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. When the downside gets concrete overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time — without an audience, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.61},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.67},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.85}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This prop-desk scalper rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. When the downside gets concrete overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time — without an audience, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4aeab7b1-a818-42c0-b122-7a6df664b4e5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.19,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Trusts momentum over preparation. This volatility arbitrageur dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the stakes rise treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — day to day, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Trusts momentum over preparation. This volatility arbitrageur dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the stakes rise treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — day to day, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2f1949d8-2b0d-4174-866e-89d248958ca1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.29,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.96},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When the number turns red, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.54},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.53},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.51},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When the number turns red, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('098f2c51-2260-44e1-aaf7-4087a83498f4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.44,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.78,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. This bonding-curve sniper reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. When the stakes rise extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — on a slow afternoon, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.44,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. This bonding-curve sniper reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. When the stakes rise extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — on a slow afternoon, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d33bae87-7c8b-4ecb-bb88-6815935d82c7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.71,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later, and when the stakes are trivial checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later, and when the stakes are trivial checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('59474b0f-10d3-41e3-9fcb-59983f7fa254', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.27,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced DeFi yield farmer: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and in the small things rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.52},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced DeFi yield farmer: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and in the small things rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0c4f09f5-49a4-457f-8908-6e3263635108', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.85,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.75,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Bonding-curve sniper, pronounced in style: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject; would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. The moment it stops being hypothetical extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Bonding-curve sniper, pronounced in style: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject; would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. The moment it stops being hypothetical extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6a283e47-5785-48fb-a1e6-f1947cb89255', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.88,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.95,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This options seller treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When the stakes rise discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — in the parts nobody grades, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This options seller treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When the stakes rise discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — in the parts nobody grades, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ec41f17f-8183-4c8c-b6cb-9d408b015081', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.18,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.71,"narcissism":0.92,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.87,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly, and when no one is watching sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.18,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly, and when no one is watching sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e4a52e50-b941-4888-97c0-35807269d999', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.84,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. This zero-DTE options gambler treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. In a pinch mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — day to day, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. This zero-DTE options gambler treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. In a pinch mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — day to day, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0c67f713-d8eb-46c4-97b8-d044ce00285d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.8},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.57,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When cornered, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a steady options seller who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and measures decisions by who they might upset. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and across the quiet stretches sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.8}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'When cornered, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a steady options seller who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and measures decisions by who they might upset. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and across the quiet stretches sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ecd4d148-adf5-488b-a155-9e0d6c7b5deb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.56,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper, steady in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. The moment it stops being hypothetical sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper, steady in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. The moment it stops being hypothetical sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('02129c98-0021-4330-b166-e2bf6f7d5827', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.71},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.45,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.46,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. Otherwise, a steady value investor who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and measures decisions by who they might upset. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the routine of it exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.61},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.59},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.71}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. Otherwise, a steady value investor who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and measures decisions by who they might upset. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the routine of it exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5284ffe8-1e31-4229-80a7-ae03e600101c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.47,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.81,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the number turns red, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a measured dividend-yield chaser who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and across the quiet stretches names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.54},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'When the number turns red, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a measured dividend-yield chaser who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and across the quiet stretches names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.8, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c1009231-4025-4337-bac4-34fb2aab49c7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.24},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.96,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured prop-desk scalper who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. When cornered overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; in the unglamorous middle of things, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.55},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.5}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.66,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A measured prop-desk scalper who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. When cornered overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; in the unglamorous middle of things, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.88, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c1856b9c-2e78-44b0-a03c-95fe5c8b75c4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.71},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.37,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Under a deadline, judges likelihood by how easily an example comes to mind, not by the base rate. Otherwise, a steady macro allocator who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and in the small things sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.6},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.55},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.71}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Under a deadline, judges likelihood by how easily an example comes to mind, not by the base rate. Otherwise, a steady macro allocator who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and in the small things sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
