('dd764d94-55d6-4201-8fb8-0591bad8cceb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.37,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Confuses motion with progress. When the safe option quietly expires, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.74},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.68},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Confuses motion with progress. When the safe option quietly expires, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b58f55fb-2acd-4a7b-a0bb-6d2e49e853db', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.4,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. A pronounced options seller: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and on an ordinary week refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.67},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. A pronounced options seller: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and on an ordinary week refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7534eb92-7816-432d-9ae8-5c3f6dd41d36', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.45,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.84,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a steady discretionary swing trader who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and when no one is watching checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.59},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.61},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.8,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a steady discretionary swing trader who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and when no one is watching checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1476a920-0db4-43d9-935d-8cc3d9aacc3b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.7},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.98,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When cornered, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.7}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When cornered, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c18d9a4a-3bcc-412b-813c-31183c0bcd3a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.34,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"MEV searcher whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Under pressure, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.48},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.5},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'MEV searcher whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Under pressure, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6f516687-3e55-4525-88ba-d83c725fbba4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.35,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced options seller who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When someone is watching the outcome finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; across the quiet stretches, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.55},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced options seller who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When someone is watching the outcome finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; across the quiet stretches, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f62e10f0-abcb-4b8a-a08a-03060b73e5e5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.27},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.52,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.22,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When the walls close in, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. Otherwise, a pronounced discretionary swing trader who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and lets others fill the silence and reads them while they do. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and in the routine of it keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.6},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.62},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.27}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'When the walls close in, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. Otherwise, a pronounced discretionary swing trader who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and lets others fill the silence and reads them while they do. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and in the routine of it keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9074ebac-f701-46d5-bd23-142db73a7462', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.21,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"The moment it stops being hypothetical, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. Otherwise, a pronounced value investor who recharges by being around people, not away from them and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and once the urgency drains out keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'The moment it stops being hypothetical, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. Otherwise, a pronounced value investor who recharges by being around people, not away from them and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and once the urgency drains out keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ed25852a-561f-40f1-b7e6-fb656dddd2f2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.75,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When someone is watching the outcome, gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns. Otherwise, a measured futures spreader who measures decisions by who they might upset and cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and when the stakes are trivial treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ESFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.5},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.58},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ESFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'When someone is watching the outcome, gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns. Otherwise, a measured futures spreader who measures decisions by who they might upset and cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and when the stakes are trivial treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.82, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ad905523-b19f-4eff-ad1f-2f751b385684', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.17,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady value investor: recharges by being around people, not away from them, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and on an ordinary week calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A steady value investor: recharges by being around people, not away from them, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and on an ordinary week calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a4148451-b6b9-4ae2-baf8-d6c2a0485346', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.37,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced delta-neutral market maker who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When cornered delays checking the number it most needs to check; on an ordinary week, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A pronounced delta-neutral market maker who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When cornered delays checking the number it most needs to check; on an ordinary week, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2f0ea6d0-2994-4113-b9c8-bd7f60e86da2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.76,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader, measured in style: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice; defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Once things get tense gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.53},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.48},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader, measured in style: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice; defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Once things get tense gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.', 0.85, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('72b80512-5e90-42de-92be-40ded30a1b9e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.75,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady options seller who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the walls close in would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; left to their own devices, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.59},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A steady options seller who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the walls close in would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; left to their own devices, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b5f7bc13-ae0e-4295-bfe1-4d346ef6da5e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.05,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This discretionary swing trader would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. The instant it becomes irreversible takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — in the parts nobody grades, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This discretionary swing trader would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. The instant it becomes irreversible takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — in the parts nobody grades, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d527e68a-1221-4a89-9da0-ed0d24b5cd42', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.44,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.19,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. This crypto day-trader chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and recharges by being around people, not away from them. In a pinch expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately — as a rule, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.44,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. This crypto day-trader chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and recharges by being around people, not away from them. In a pinch expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately — as a rule, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f3b291d0-76ae-4239-8d86-4ed591c5a432', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.75},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.28,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense. A steady delta-neutral market maker: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the version no one reviews keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.61},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.75}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense. A steady delta-neutral market maker: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the version no one reviews keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('cf950631-5bc3-495a-acc9-fb996b415764', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.19,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.5,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced discretionary swing trader who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When the safe option quietly expires treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; when the pressure is off, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.19,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced discretionary swing trader who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When the safe option quietly expires treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; when the pressure is off, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c35db7e7-afaa-4c24-a483-9fd75f7e1182', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.9,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.77,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis, and once the urgency drains out sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis, and once the urgency drains out sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('594f1ae0-503c-4199-a485-fdd121e46ceb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.05,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A steady prop-desk scalper: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it, treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Trusts momentum over preparation, and in the small things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A steady prop-desk scalper: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it, treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Trusts momentum over preparation, and in the small things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('67c7548b-504b-4dcb-805e-9d26fd47d3f1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.28,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.44,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Crypto day-trader, pronounced in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. When the stakes rise looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.67},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader, pronounced in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. When the stakes rise looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6ccea2f2-ff27-4870-bc96-ffe69e8d929c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. A steady bonding-curve sniper: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, confuses motion with progress. Trusts momentum over preparation, and day to day keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. A steady bonding-curve sniper: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, confuses motion with progress. Trusts momentum over preparation, and day to day keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('cf1b5abd-c22a-4c87-a72d-0894ee7de39c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.96,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.85,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.99,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. The moment it stops being hypothetical, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.76},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.96,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. The moment it stops being hypothetical, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3fd029fb-e05e-480d-8b71-7fd9e1b6002a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.81,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This DeFi yield farmer reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and recharges by being around people, not away from them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line assumes the current streak is the new normal — without an audience, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This DeFi yield farmer reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and recharges by being around people, not away from them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line assumes the current streak is the new normal — without an audience, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('cb88a805-267e-4d3d-a013-02c1556f1020', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.76},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.56,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This penny-stock gambler carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Under a deadline locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense — in the parts nobody grades, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.76}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This penny-stock gambler carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Under a deadline locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense — in the parts nobody grades, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('99c1f5a6-5a5c-4bda-ba23-ecc7b6306e54', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.67,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.73,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Pairs trader, pronounced in style: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system; fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. The instant the deadline moves up discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Pairs trader, pronounced in style: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system; fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. The instant the deadline moves up discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('26713efa-a3ba-43b5-aaa7-4fd185e080ed', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.88,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced value investor who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. In a pinch assumes the current streak is the new normal; left to their own devices, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced value investor who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. In a pinch assumes the current streak is the new normal; left to their own devices, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2e382f86-0e86-4efe-8b1a-8896cee38d40', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.45,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.32,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.74,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A steady value investor: finds a full day of meetings more draining than a full day of work, over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and left to their own devices trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.58},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.45,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.32,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A steady value investor: finds a full day of meetings more draining than a full day of work, over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and left to their own devices trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('014b8012-fed5-416e-939c-81604332951b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When the walls close in, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced onchain copy-trader who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and across the quiet stretches averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.55},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.6},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'When the walls close in, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced onchain copy-trader who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and across the quiet stretches averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('754f7e8a-f5ce-4241-b2f8-e699318019c8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.05,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Futures spreader whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Trusts momentum over preparation. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. When there is no clean exit, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.73},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Futures spreader whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Trusts momentum over preparation. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. When there is no clean exit, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('087b3713-a2c4-42b6-837e-b7ef2ae0e946', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.18,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.95,"psychopathy":0.68},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.81,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader, pronounced in style: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system; fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. When the safe option quietly expires is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.18,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader, pronounced in style: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system; fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. When the safe option quietly expires is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('366d97fd-f159-4267-b14f-88e0455061d7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.18,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced bonding-curve sniper who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When there is no clean exit underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; when the pressure is off, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.58},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.52},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced bonding-curve sniper who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When there is no clean exit underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; when the pressure is off, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('67fbb777-823a-41f8-9aff-0ef268b017de', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.33},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced prop-desk scalper who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. The moment risk appears assumes the current streak is the new normal; on a slow afternoon, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.33}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced prop-desk scalper who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. The moment risk appears assumes the current streak is the new normal; on a slow afternoon, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('411a3bcc-3efc-4c69-8e4b-86bc5a9b8345', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.95,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.94,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.69,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Under a deadline, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who recharges by being around people, not away from them and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet, and once the urgency drains out calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.95,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','outgoing']::text[], 'Under a deadline, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who recharges by being around people, not away from them and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet, and once the urgency drains out calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7882dd0e-ac25-4364-9715-5aa154469715', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.35},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.42,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. The moment it stops being hypothetical, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.59},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.35}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. The moment it stops being hypothetical, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('36a1e7f2-8261-4ccd-8205-147f60d4a4ea', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.87,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This MEV searcher chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the walls close in jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — day to day, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This MEV searcher chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the walls close in jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — day to day, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('14db727e-7052-4a3b-8309-7ee936c9b8e5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.2,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.95,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.68,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.96},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced crypto day-trader who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. The instant the deadline moves up takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; in the small things, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.2,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced crypto day-trader who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. The instant the deadline moves up takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; in the small things, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('14ad593d-72af-44a9-a2c0-52efaa8235bc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.2,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.89,"psychopathy":0.65},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.05,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced options seller who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. The moment it stops being hypothetical discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; day to day, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.2,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced options seller who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. The moment it stops being hypothetical discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; day to day, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('74896dd4-4c06-486f-818a-76b27209b0c4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.78,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The moment risk appears, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a pronounced perps degen who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet, and in the small things keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a pronounced perps degen who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet, and in the small things keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e89f2acc-c9fa-4bda-a45d-56e9742152c0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.96,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.31},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.79,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.15,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation, says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and across an ordinary week refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.96,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.31}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation, says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and across an ordinary week refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a59ad682-b64a-4938-aef1-a535f6008733', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.34},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.28,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about. A pronounced pairs trader: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and in the small things talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.56},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.34}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about. A pronounced pairs trader: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and in the small things talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('acb846b8-72a8-4ef9-a04c-1196d3db7903', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.28},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.36,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced MEV searcher who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. The instant the deadline moves up underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; in the version no one reviews, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","open-minded","temperament"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.28}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','open-minded','temperament']::text[], 'A pronounced MEV searcher who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. The instant the deadline moves up underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; in the version no one reviews, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('253b5380-be7a-49f5-920a-780e52b95e52', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.17,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced penny-stock gambler who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Under pressure discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; across the quiet stretches, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.57},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.55},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced penny-stock gambler who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Under pressure discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; across the quiet stretches, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f2b9db0d-44b2-4ff2-8417-77fa361847c7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.72,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When cornered, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a steady delta-neutral market maker who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and in the small things holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'When cornered, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a steady delta-neutral market maker who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and in the small things holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4b3f0e3e-a4d1-4ec5-b9ad-9083109369ff', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.51,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.92,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. This pairs trader collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Under pressure jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — without an audience, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. This pairs trader collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Under pressure jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — without an audience, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c4889ca7-568f-4bed-966a-05f387a7b64f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.41,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Retail momentum chaser, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the number turns red treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Retail momentum chaser, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the number turns red treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
