('c7ddf822-c470-43ec-b6ee-0b002c5ca5c7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.88},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.27,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.65,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This algorithmic market-maker spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Once things get tense delays checking the number it most needs to check — in the version no one reviews, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.75},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.69},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.88}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. This algorithmic market-maker spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Once things get tense delays checking the number it most needs to check — in the version no one reviews, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('07b2395e-5ba9-4827-b618-09d49003eb4f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.73,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A measured perps degen: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly, cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the pattern nobody else tracks trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.52},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. A measured perps degen: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly, cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the pattern nobody else tracks trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.89, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2d99a929-f61d-4121-b200-742d974bfed9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.94},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.7,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one. A pronounced prop-desk scalper: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and when the pressure is off confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.71},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.94}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one. A pronounced prop-desk scalper: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and when the pressure is off confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c7c0015e-c2a7-4c63-b10b-fa92228257ee', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.39},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Under pressure, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced prop-desk scalper who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and when the pressure is off screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.39}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Under pressure, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced prop-desk scalper who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and when the pressure is off screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c7e33c1f-41a8-477e-930f-89faa050d877', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.73,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Lets the deadline make the decision by default. This bonding-curve sniper rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the walls close in delays checking the number it most needs to check — when the pressure is off, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Lets the deadline make the decision by default. This bonding-curve sniper rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the walls close in delays checking the number it most needs to check — when the pressure is off, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
