('332d3165-d560-4aca-a2aa-24c46afc9b22', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.7,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady value investor who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. Optimizes for winning over being liked. When cornered adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; on a slow afternoon, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A steady value investor who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. Optimizes for winning over being liked. When cornered adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; on a slow afternoon, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b5312818-d81b-4472-8420-2e6f682432c4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.45,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.89,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the downside gets concrete, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and without an audience backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.56},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'When the downside gets concrete, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and without an audience backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7ebcdbe6-d9bf-4220-8c36-fe8604a8375b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.49,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.02,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced meme-coin rotator who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. The moment risk appears mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; in the small things, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced meme-coin rotator who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. The moment risk appears mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; in the small things, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c6e20933-187c-4f6e-ab0a-b3b00efe7e86', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.53,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.23,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced meme-coin rotator who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the safe option quietly expires extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; in the unglamorous middle of things, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced meme-coin rotator who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the safe option quietly expires extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; in the unglamorous middle of things, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7d805c2c-9970-4422-a57e-73ecf01c727b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. When the safe option quietly expires takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. When the safe option quietly expires takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('76adadc9-1c0a-4c5f-a3e0-65d60e03f6a7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. A pronounced pairs trader: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences, and in the unglamorous middle of things averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. A pronounced pairs trader: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences, and in the unglamorous middle of things averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0583924e-7afb-452f-b1a1-f52fefda9fc2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.23},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.63},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.27,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This discretionary swing trader builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. Once things get tense is more certain than the hit rate justifies — day to day, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.23}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This discretionary swing trader builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. Once things get tense is more certain than the hit rate justifies — day to day, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
