('e297ad0d-4a69-4ad6-9741-269cf445d645', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.05,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"DeFi yield farmer, steady in style: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. When there is no clean exit finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'DeFi yield farmer, steady in style: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. When there is no clean exit finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('17f7d9dd-9a1e-400c-a4fd-46672311d9e3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.58,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.74},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Under pressure, guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and in the small things apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Under pressure, guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and in the small things apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('156be7c6-d0d5-4bf1-b7c0-e7553c5b5e5c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.37,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.5,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.17,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Under a deadline, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and when no one is watching holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.37,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Under a deadline, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and when no one is watching holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7737e41e-ba15-4547-991e-18c874cd13d1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The moment it stops being hypothetical, defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence. Otherwise, a steady bonding-curve sniper who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and day to day screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.58},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.58},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'The moment it stops being hypothetical, defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence. Otherwise, a steady bonding-curve sniper who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and day to day screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('72da4e61-a604-4c69-bc9f-f4d36335979f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.9},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.71,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long. A pronounced perps degen: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and when the stakes are trivial holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.73},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.9}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long. A pronounced perps degen: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and when the stakes are trivial holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d1d12c02-c976-424f-9062-061f27fdfedd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.85,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Once things get tense, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.9,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Once things get tense, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8080db76-8daa-4c7b-9898-7a957a3b9bab', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.03,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Options seller whose defining move is that they absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. In a pinch, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.5},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.49}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Options seller whose defining move is that they absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. In a pinch, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.83, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0219bd44-cb63-43ab-a522-745f92d888bb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.88,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.83,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"MEV searcher whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Once things get tense, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'MEV searcher whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Once things get tense, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9693fed4-248e-4734-9abb-6f0612d768a2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.87,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. This pairs trader gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and optimizes for winning over being liked. When there is no clean exit finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — left to their own devices, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.58},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. This pairs trader gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and optimizes for winning over being liked. When there is no clean exit finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — left to their own devices, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('cbea940f-dc13-4e7b-8492-d56d7ad86573', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.45,"neuroticism":0.2},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.44,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.45,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about. A pronounced airdrop farmer: maintains flawless records nobody asked for, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and on a slow afternoon talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.6},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.45,"neuroticism":0.2}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'Discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about. A pronounced airdrop farmer: maintains flawless records nobody asked for, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and on a slow afternoon talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a3f26c3c-5a76-4224-bbb9-c5165510cb4b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.43,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and in the version no one reviews talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.43,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and in the version no one reviews talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4e934396-02f3-4898-9729-a5196db28d94', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.95},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.72,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. The moment it stops being hypothetical, feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.69},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.95}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. The moment it stops being hypothetical, feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b304c0e7-b340-4647-99b9-f90488536979', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.45,"neuroticism":0.34},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.15,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This futures spreader gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When the safe option quietly expires cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — in the routine of it, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.53},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.45,"neuroticism":0.34}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This futures spreader gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When the safe option quietly expires cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — in the routine of it, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('af6c56b9-a396-4f21-9c82-8fc85df645f3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.92,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A steady macro allocator: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly, and across an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A steady macro allocator: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly, and across an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b2b540de-0833-43a0-92e3-9fb46d712e5e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.24,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur whose defining move is that they rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Once things get tense, judges likelihood by how easily an example comes to mind, not by the base rate; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.64},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur whose defining move is that they rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Once things get tense, judges likelihood by how easily an example comes to mind, not by the base rate; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9e46ee52-2ca8-4bab-8d7c-767644b76741', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.9,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.76,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Airdrop farmer, pronounced in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. The moment risk appears assumes the current streak is the new normal.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Airdrop farmer, pronounced in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. The moment risk appears assumes the current streak is the new normal.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('52df527e-ffe1-41c2-a97b-25bdf25f43d2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.29},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.08,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced prop-desk scalper who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Confuses motion with progress. When the stakes rise underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; as a rule, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.6},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.29}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced prop-desk scalper who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Confuses motion with progress. When the stakes rise underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; as a rule, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
