('e9ad72b2-3d40-4e66-b6b0-38e4c2d73deb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.7,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.86,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"In a pinch, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and in the parts nobody grades keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.76},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'In a pinch, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and in the parts nobody grades keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('02d750ff-b44a-4969-a762-b4d9246f75fc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.18},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.64},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.28,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Perps degen, pronounced in style: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work; treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. The instant the deadline moves up underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.69},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.18}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Perps degen, pronounced in style: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work; treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. The instant the deadline moves up underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3dfadee6-078d-4ddc-b7f1-fec7bfab24f2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.83,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.76,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis, and in the version no one reviews holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis, and in the version no one reviews holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6938eff3-0826-4b5f-861e-f2ef5f6d2759', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.67,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When the walls close in, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a steady algorithmic market-maker who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the pattern nobody else tracks confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'When the walls close in, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a steady algorithmic market-maker who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and in the pattern nobody else tracks confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b09609ae-bbcd-4ed0-83a0-60a722bfb8a9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.49,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Futures spreader whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. The instant it becomes irreversible, delays checking the number it most needs to check; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.73},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Futures spreader whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. The instant it becomes irreversible, delays checking the number it most needs to check; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('97ab2322-746f-4eb8-b877-44e20c76a252', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.68},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.86,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Measures decisions by who they might upset. Under pressure, assumes the current streak is the new normal; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.68}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Measures decisions by who they might upset. Under pressure, assumes the current streak is the new normal; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
