('cd9489af-63d3-4b33-94a0-90c9984a73d5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.66},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.46,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Value investor whose defining move is that they maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. The instant it becomes irreversible, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'Value investor whose defining move is that they maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. The instant it becomes irreversible, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6d587397-e6fe-4e1c-8434-095d9fd88b8e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.97,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.34,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.08,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Futures spreader whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Once the exit narrows to one door, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.8},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.78},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.97,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Futures spreader whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Once the exit narrows to one door, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a58b02fa-1792-477f-8b2e-b0e121de71c2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.85},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.7,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced retail momentum chaser who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Confuses motion with progress. Once the exit narrows to one door delays checking the number it most needs to check; once the urgency drains out, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.75},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.85}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced retail momentum chaser who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Confuses motion with progress. Once the exit narrows to one door delays checking the number it most needs to check; once the urgency drains out, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('df497935-3588-42a2-a039-b9a0d488a359', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.2,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.87,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.83,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced index-fund holdout who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. The instant the deadline moves up extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; when no one is watching, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.2,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced index-fund holdout who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. The instant the deadline moves up extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; when no one is watching, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2a3dda51-e1a6-4274-a784-196ebb1564b0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.95,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the walls close in, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced perps degen who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and in the parts nobody grades trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.51},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'When the walls close in, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced perps degen who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and in the parts nobody grades trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('40bfc896-ba20-4bc0-aa0b-05c61a2bb39d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.44,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.44,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Under a deadline, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and once the urgency drains out sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.57},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Under a deadline, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a steady retail momentum chaser who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and once the urgency drains out sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f0e5147d-c889-491d-a455-493cd88bcc66', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.03,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured crypto day-trader who measures decisions by who they might upset. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; without an audience, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.51},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.52},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A measured crypto day-trader who measures decisions by who they might upset. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; without an audience, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.89, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d8724301-2b78-40fa-ab4e-9ee4a18ae469', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.51,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.19,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced prop-desk scalper who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the pattern nobody else tracks calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced prop-desk scalper who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the pattern nobody else tracks calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7776bc37-eb2e-4699-9805-6b1b0749bb2f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.89},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.61,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This meme-coin rotator needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. The instant the deadline moves up will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one — without an audience, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.61},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.66},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.89}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This meme-coin rotator needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. The instant the deadline moves up will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one — without an audience, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9a05cecd-f177-4841-9b6c-d66a786c32a7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.16},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.74},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.28,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. In a pinch, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.73},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.16}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. In a pinch, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1beb21e5-eefc-4413-b2b2-c4518670aadb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.56,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense. A steady commodities speculator: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and in the small things averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense. A steady commodities speculator: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and in the small things averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d9ded295-913f-495b-9927-44730e82c71d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.31},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.42,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Under pressure, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. Otherwise, a pronounced discretionary swing trader who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and day to day backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.51},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.53},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.61},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.31}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'Under pressure, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. Otherwise, a pronounced discretionary swing trader who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and day to day backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('249d11cb-2aab-4fc2-818f-9659f5e43e09', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. A pronounced crypto day-trader: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and as a rule refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. A pronounced crypto day-trader: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and as a rule refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('651470b5-e955-466e-bc4f-76349bb42312', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.73,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.51,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.86,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Liquidation-bot operator, steady in style: cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. The moment it stops being hypothetical gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.49},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.51},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.73,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Liquidation-bot operator, steady in style: cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. The moment it stops being hypothetical gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('eaed8e68-ee89-45ca-86d6-e9b39a3ab2e8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.87,"extraversion":0.34,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.28},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.53,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.26,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When the stakes rise, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. Otherwise, a pronounced onchain copy-trader who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and across an ordinary week keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.64},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.53},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.87,"extraversion":0.34,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.28}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. Otherwise, a pronounced onchain copy-trader who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and across an ordinary week keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e4e58693-4c4a-4e59-afbd-30736a65560f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.44,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.54,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Airdrop farmer whose defining move is that they rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Under pressure, guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.59},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Airdrop farmer whose defining move is that they rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Under pressure, guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('51ab08b4-e1c5-4bb3-a446-e250df718916', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This futures spreader chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When the number turns red discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — in the pattern nobody else tracks, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.75},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This futures spreader chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When the number turns red discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — in the pattern nobody else tracks, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6cb3124a-6cc6-4a1d-adc9-c9ea89314c55', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.82,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured index-fund holdout who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Under pressure gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; as a rule, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.51},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.47}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A measured index-fund holdout who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right. Under pressure gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; as a rule, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.81, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('44b7fa97-6cb9-484e-98e5-9eed3f569b5b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.33,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.3},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.84,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.47,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Macro allocator, pronounced in style: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice; treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Under pressure underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.69},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.33,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.3}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Macro allocator, pronounced in style: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice; treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Under pressure underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('499fd8b0-56d0-4d6c-b3ac-647d4b8e1af3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.23,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A steady macro allocator: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, confuses motion with progress. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and on an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.65},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A steady macro allocator: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, confuses motion with progress. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and on an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3a762edd-d752-4770-a4bb-c1bb07db1f16', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.21,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser, steady in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. When the safe option quietly expires assumes the current streak is the new normal.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser, steady in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. When the safe option quietly expires assumes the current streak is the new normal.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9e8e6a5b-7d93-4bf4-885a-f26496ec1f24', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.73,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. The moment risk appears, feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.65},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.6},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. The moment risk appears, feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('210f5d9e-a687-4a70-a8e0-63c636d5930e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.96},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced pairs trader who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. When the downside gets concrete assumes the current streak is the new normal; when no one is watching, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.56},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced pairs trader who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. When the downside gets concrete assumes the current streak is the new normal; when no one is watching, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('18fe1ef4-7326-4cbb-87f2-badc8b83129c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"The moment it stops being hypothetical, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a steady penny-stock gambler who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and when the stakes are trivial holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.48}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'The moment it stops being hypothetical, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. Otherwise, a steady penny-stock gambler who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and when the stakes are trivial holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b2f0fef3-61ba-4cc1-a460-03a14e5d35af', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.53,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator whose defining move is that they notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Under a deadline, assumes the current streak is the new normal; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.58},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator whose defining move is that they notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Under a deadline, assumes the current streak is the new normal; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('af5e9ab1-fdc4-4f7b-addf-0442301d3dd7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.86,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the walls close in, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. Otherwise, a pronounced index-fund holdout who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and without an audience averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing']::text[], 'When the walls close in, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. Otherwise, a pronounced index-fund holdout who dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and without an audience averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9fe2d320-4407-4875-92a2-aceb65f6e065', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.76,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced value investor: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence, confuses motion with progress. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and day to day names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced value investor: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence, confuses motion with progress. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and day to day names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('cd9ea869-b4a6-40c7-ac6a-7d0d9fdfb45a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.91,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Options seller whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.58},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Options seller whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9c8fd90b-609b-4c05-8069-52cfe933a0c7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.77,"extraversion":0.27,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.24},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.85,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This volatility arbitrageur cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and measures decisions by who they might upset. Under pressure second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees — without an audience, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.53},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.55},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.57},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.5}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.77,"extraversion":0.27,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. This volatility arbitrageur cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and measures decisions by who they might upset. Under pressure second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees — without an audience, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('54588615-4c9c-4e92-bdce-417152dc97a4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.73,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Lets the deadline make the decision by default. This delta-neutral market maker needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. In a pinch looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — across an ordinary week, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.56},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Lets the deadline make the decision by default. This delta-neutral market maker needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. In a pinch looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — across an ordinary week, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('77be27b2-860e-402f-9a36-bec3a92700d3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.54,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This value investor hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When the walls close in sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long — in the unglamorous middle of things, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This value investor hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When the walls close in sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long — in the unglamorous middle of things, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b2752639-b5cc-479b-825e-aaa814df27aa', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.77,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker, steady in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. When the downside gets concrete gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker, steady in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. When the downside gets concrete gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it.', 0.86, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bbf1f524-d197-4ba8-a990-b646aea3f64f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.76},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.39,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady meme-coin rotator who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When someone is watching the outcome would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; in the parts nobody grades, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.56},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.61},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.76}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A steady meme-coin rotator who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When someone is watching the outcome would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; in the parts nobody grades, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.89, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('86dbe103-8529-41ca-a0a1-9b468c611880', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.54,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Value investor whose defining move is that they spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the safe option quietly expires, guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains; apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.66},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.69},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Value investor whose defining move is that they spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the safe option quietly expires, guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains; apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('03468f0d-f493-4265-953e-8bce70d78150', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.9},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.52,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.74},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. This onchain copy-trader hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the downside gets concrete would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — on a slow afternoon, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.81},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.74},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.9}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. This onchain copy-trader hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the downside gets concrete would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — on a slow afternoon, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ddda3ade-0d8e-4736-8d58-70567c2858ff', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.85,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a pronounced dividend-yield chaser who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and across an ordinary week names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a pronounced dividend-yield chaser who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and across an ordinary week names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a8070cd9-8b23-4f8e-a1b8-883942115583', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.8,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. A pronounced prop-desk scalper: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and in the version no one reviews sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.72},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. A pronounced prop-desk scalper: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and in the version no one reviews sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('deaaabf1-1296-4d55-a521-fa6759096459', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Liquidation-bot operator, steady in style: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. When the safe option quietly expires is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Liquidation-bot operator, steady in style: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. When the safe option quietly expires is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4ef69525-4635-4a0f-bc09-651b6d15b217', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.23,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A steady index-fund holdout: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences, and when the pressure is off talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. A steady index-fund holdout: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences, and when the pressure is off talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c7b61457-07df-4372-a4f9-de36a614c480', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.87},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.74,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A pronounced retail momentum chaser: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and in the pattern nobody else tracks sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.78},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.87}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A pronounced retail momentum chaser: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and in the pattern nobody else tracks sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('514d9c35-4522-4af3-aee4-65f60a734751', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.22,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur, pronounced in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. When the safe option quietly expires finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur, pronounced in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. When the safe option quietly expires finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1c5922e4-dfa4-4880-b5b8-52570b357b5a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.17,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Wants the base rate before the anecdote. This algorithmic market-maker chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Once things get tense abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — without an audience, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.55},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Wants the base rate before the anecdote. This algorithmic market-maker chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Once things get tense abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — without an audience, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0c9aa3e3-4a4e-4591-9d4f-14e9fc1c49ec', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.37,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This MEV searcher reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Under a deadline discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — when the pressure is off, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.53},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This MEV searcher reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Under a deadline discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — when the pressure is off, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('35795d37-9666-4d56-a93a-045604147d10', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.17,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.96,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A steady macro allocator: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and in the routine of it sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.17,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A steady macro allocator: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and in the routine of it sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('56e8b436-ecea-4b01-a537-cad988771fb8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.47,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.75,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A steady penny-stock gambler: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and day to day treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.62},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A steady penny-stock gambler: absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and day to day treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('597c8a83-4160-42c9-9a73-577df84e2019', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.77,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. When cornered weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.63},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.61},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. When cornered weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f8e343bf-f7b0-4d7a-9df5-36e234183f1c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.39},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.3,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about. Otherwise, a pronounced pairs trader who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the unglamorous middle of things calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.55},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.39}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about. Otherwise, a pronounced pairs trader who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the unglamorous middle of things calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('32a4e9da-989f-4be8-82e3-b634c8af7532', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.78,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Once the exit narrows to one door, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.57},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Once the exit narrows to one door, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8b8da2b6-6aa4-47c0-b3a4-77fe1a5cf6f7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.95,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced penny-stock gambler who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. The moment it stops being hypothetical jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; in the pattern nobody else tracks, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'A pronounced penny-stock gambler who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. The moment it stops being hypothetical jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; in the pattern nobody else tracks, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('15a634e8-05bc-4973-aead-2e22d4792b2a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.91,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.99,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Once the exit narrows to one door, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Once the exit narrows to one door, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5b3d82fd-4883-4900-9aa1-66a11e233037', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.1,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This discretionary swing trader treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When the safe option quietly expires jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — in the parts nobody grades, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This discretionary swing trader treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When the safe option quietly expires jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — in the parts nobody grades, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b48bcc78-036e-4797-ba73-01644732f829', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.18,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.7,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This quant researcher collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the walls close in assumes the current streak is the new normal — day to day, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.6},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.18,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This quant researcher collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the walls close in assumes the current streak is the new normal — day to day, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1e661fb0-eb0e-467f-8363-2a218a041d37', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.9,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced retail momentum chaser who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When the stakes rise cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; on a slow afternoon, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced retail momentum chaser who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When the stakes rise cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; on a slow afternoon, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f149d4a8-68d2-4b4c-8533-bc0d126a8dda', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.14,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced prop-desk scalper: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and when the pressure is off confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. A pronounced prop-desk scalper: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and when the pressure is off confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('012d677c-37e5-4e0b-b6b5-bc12d56dae08', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.87},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.72,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. This airdrop farmer hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. The instant it becomes irreversible feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused — across the quiet stretches, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.64},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.67},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.73},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.87}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. This airdrop farmer hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. The instant it becomes irreversible feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused — across the quiet stretches, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3b4e2460-9fc3-4030-afa3-9220532517c6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.87},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.52,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and without an audience screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.87}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and without an audience screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f5fe36eb-68f1-4177-8282-63d4c9ba7a2e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.97,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.94,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.85,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader, pronounced in style: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet; negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.81},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.83}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.97,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader, pronounced in style: dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet; negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e96e20d8-8598-46d2-aa63-27dbc508cae3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.31,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. This bonding-curve sniper reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Once the exit narrows to one door assumes the current streak is the new normal — across the quiet stretches, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. This bonding-curve sniper reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Once the exit narrows to one door assumes the current streak is the new normal — across the quiet stretches, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('64c70c34-8460-4a0e-b42c-4527c58fd570', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.17,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Once the exit narrows to one door, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.54},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.5},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator whose defining move is that they gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Once the exit narrows to one door, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bb86b14d-8c23-4bd0-8f2c-9ee287b60a1a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.93,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the number turns red, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a steady meme-coin rotator who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and when the pressure is off treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.53},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.58},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'When the number turns red, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a steady meme-coin rotator who takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and when the pressure is off treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c2ad7fa1-f8b8-4841-988a-78fdabd0c4c2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.02,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced macro allocator who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts momentum over preparation. Reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. When the downside gets concrete is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; in the routine of it, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.81}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'A pronounced macro allocator who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Trusts momentum over preparation. Reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. When the downside gets concrete is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; in the routine of it, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f0a540f4-6375-4b2e-b0de-a785f7d86704', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.13},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.86,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.63},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.44,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and on a slow afternoon apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.7},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.13}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'Underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and on a slow afternoon apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
