('a5e71c76-9fc8-4cf4-b353-49cb71c332eb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.45,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.53,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Lets the deadline make the decision by default. This quant researcher needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and recharges by being around people, not away from them. When the stakes rise discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — when the pressure is off, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.57},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.68},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Lets the deadline make the decision by default. This quant researcher needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and recharges by being around people, not away from them. When the stakes rise discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — when the pressure is off, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('70060b5c-71e2-4f33-8f62-0fba399c0e63', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.6,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Perps degen, pronounced in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision; gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the downside gets concrete cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Perps degen, pronounced in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision; gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. When the downside gets concrete cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('592e3e14-d514-40e2-b02c-e10befaf2401', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.92},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.25,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.49,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.72},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"The moment it stops being hypothetical, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and in the pattern nobody else tracks treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.92}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'The moment it stops being hypothetical, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and in the pattern nobody else tracks treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5ed2e4f1-e755-47d4-ac65-a4bb638c11a1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.37,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper, steady in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. When the stakes rise treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper, steady in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. When the stakes rise treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('cf57d125-ba92-4079-84a5-d784c57001d2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.34},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.29,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This prop-desk scalper treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. When someone is watching the outcome holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support — as a rule, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.53},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.34}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This prop-desk scalper treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. When someone is watching the outcome holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support — as a rule, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6217b119-84f8-4c6c-b4ee-25440cbd4033', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.81,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. This options seller reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. When the safe option quietly expires discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — in the version no one reviews, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.76},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. This options seller reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. When the safe option quietly expires discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — in the version no one reviews, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1be4c352-24d5-46a6-b841-363d5f88e9a8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.94,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.68},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.05,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Futures spreader whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Trusts momentum over preparation. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.77}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.94,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.68}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Futures spreader whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Trusts momentum over preparation. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3232805a-54d9-4524-95b9-fc58948f4a31', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.86,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Trusts momentum over preparation. Leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Once the exit narrows to one door, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Trusts momentum over preparation. Leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Once the exit narrows to one door, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9162ae80-9e55-4f9e-891b-0bf127dfae61', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.12,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When the stakes rise, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a pronounced meme-coin rotator who narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and in the routine of it treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.76},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.78},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a pronounced meme-coin rotator who narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and in the routine of it treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('72a88f5d-2781-4edd-80a3-73792c900e68', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.15,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When someone is watching the outcome, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When someone is watching the outcome, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('66729db9-2ff3-4a8b-a0ad-95129dbdb406', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler, pronounced in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Once things get tense abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.52},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler, pronounced in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Once things get tense abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d7a55d7e-3e2e-458a-a976-ea6006338896', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.47,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This onchain copy-trader hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line delays checking the number it most needs to check — in the routine of it, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.63},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This onchain copy-trader hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line delays checking the number it most needs to check — in the routine of it, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9434f4f4-97a0-430d-918f-0b3a72f87cbb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.83,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced MEV searcher who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Confuses motion with progress. When the number turns red cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; day to day, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.73},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced MEV searcher who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Confuses motion with progress. When the number turns red cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; day to day, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('65e04e15-8f21-4277-a2a1-0bb5a0ea91eb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.29,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and in the routine of it treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.77},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A pronounced algorithmic market-maker: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and in the routine of it treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f692e2d4-e6cb-4e19-9a7c-e4b3f1043d75', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.14,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and when the stakes are trivial treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.76},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and when the stakes are trivial treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('538ade67-ae5c-45a0-9e97-5b0e6e3f4d73', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains. A measured retail momentum chaser: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and when the stakes are trivial averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.54},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.44}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains. A measured retail momentum chaser: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and when the stakes are trivial averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.81, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('13db3766-2736-4b7d-86ec-0d477d62d9d3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.72,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.02,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence. A steady airdrop farmer: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation, measures decisions by who they might upset. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and day to day rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.5},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.59},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.48}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.72,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence. A steady airdrop farmer: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation, measures decisions by who they might upset. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and day to day rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
