('9ec7102e-bfa1-4a63-8650-5ac4e4f34ccd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.97},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.48,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced onchain copy-trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. In a pinch looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; on an ordinary week, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.76},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.71},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.8}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.97}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A pronounced onchain copy-trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. In a pinch looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; on an ordinary week, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('cb267c4f-1c86-479c-9e1d-7fb718e3e274', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.96,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.27},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.63},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.38,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When the walls close in, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.55},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.96,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.27}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When the walls close in, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9ddfbc94-c134-47af-ad32-74d12a181ed7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.84,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady volatility arbitrageur who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Once things get tense mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; across the quiet stretches, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A steady volatility arbitrageur who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Once things get tense mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; across the quiet stretches, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('54244893-bb7b-4cf1-9439-aef4f7894022', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.9,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.92,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced bonding-curve sniper who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the safe option quietly expires cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; on an ordinary week, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced bonding-curve sniper who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the safe option quietly expires cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; on an ordinary week, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e5ae1182-d77b-447a-8c0d-22e039c791c4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.24},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.94,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Retail momentum chaser, measured in style: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns; measures decisions by who they might upset. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. The moment risk appears finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.5},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Retail momentum chaser, measured in style: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns; measures decisions by who they might upset. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. The moment risk appears finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.', 0.86, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6d32909b-faeb-4794-9c39-02299accc017', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.37},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.83,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.15,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A steady penny-stock gambler who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Once the exit narrows to one door holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; in the parts nobody grades, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.37}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','outgoing']::text[], 'A steady penny-stock gambler who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Once the exit narrows to one door holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; in the parts nobody grades, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('44ace598-644d-41ea-ad12-addcbd6ebf04', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This prop-desk scalper reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When the number turns red extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — in the routine of it, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.52},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This prop-desk scalper reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When the number turns red extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — in the routine of it, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3c9b0c3e-1582-4d5f-9030-c70ccb0f4ae6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.45,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced options seller: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and when the pressure is off keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.53},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.45,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced options seller: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and when the pressure is off keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
