('9e3d41b8-985c-4045-81f1-4738814e6508', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.45,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.07,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This meme-coin rotator treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. When the downside gets concrete finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — across an ordinary week, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.46},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.45},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.46},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.64,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. This meme-coin rotator treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. When the downside gets concrete finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — across an ordinary week, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.86, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('50f39cd3-c262-4d08-8cba-86de0747fe43', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.89},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.54,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser, pronounced in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. The moment it stops being hypothetical looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.71},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.74},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.89}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser, pronounced in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. The moment it stops being hypothetical looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4409564b-40e3-4e36-8ba5-f0ce172002c5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.75},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.46,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.72,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker, steady in style: is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden; reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.75}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker, steady in style: is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden; reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense.', 0.89, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5cbfa0f3-2707-4f20-a1da-668ea8e63040', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.92},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.48,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A pronounced commodities speculator: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and once the urgency drains out treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.76},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.81},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.92}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A pronounced commodities speculator: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and once the urgency drains out treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d3550796-3f9a-4749-b310-2f69ebb2310a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced algorithmic market-maker who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line assumes the current streak is the new normal; when the stakes are trivial, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced algorithmic market-maker who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line assumes the current streak is the new normal; when the stakes are trivial, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5042ab71-eb9c-4a68-a737-889c2e93a013', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.89,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and when the stakes are trivial refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and when the stakes are trivial refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1ac4ccdc-00f5-4e49-a72b-0ea5fe8c7394', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.74,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When cornered assumes the current streak is the new normal; in the parts nobody grades, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.54},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When cornered assumes the current streak is the new normal; in the parts nobody grades, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('130dd95b-0b73-4871-9186-db31f4080d9b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.62,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This quant researcher notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Under a deadline assumes the current streak is the new normal — in the routine of it, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This quant researcher notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Under a deadline assumes the current streak is the new normal — in the routine of it, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6109b1a0-d4a4-43a3-841d-9c5c03414cee', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.36,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When the downside gets concrete, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced DeFi yield farmer who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and optimizes for winning over being liked. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and on a slow afternoon sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.54},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'When the downside gets concrete, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced DeFi yield farmer who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and optimizes for winning over being liked. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and on a slow afternoon sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b8848199-b6b9-4ec7-a794-0b8acdeda2d7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.29},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.79,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.19,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Commodities speculator whose defining move is that they front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. When the stakes rise, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.7},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.56},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.29}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'Commodities speculator whose defining move is that they front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. When the stakes rise, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('82e37ed2-38b9-4198-b2f8-41336baaec90', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.85,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they measures decisions by who they might upset. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. When the safe option quietly expires, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.52},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.49},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.47}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they measures decisions by who they might upset. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. When the safe option quietly expires, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ef430514-5f71-48ac-a79b-8291407acfa5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.76,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced discretionary swing trader: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Trusts momentum over preparation, and on an ordinary week checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced discretionary swing trader: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Trusts momentum over preparation, and on an ordinary week checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4')
