('c56f854d-61b1-411f-a696-699fda271dc0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.7,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one. A steady MEV searcher: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and day to day sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one. A steady MEV searcher: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and day to day sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0ca6430d-7b8a-486b-ab82-5753ba70a2ef', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. When the safe option quietly expires, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.73},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.78},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.8}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.91,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. When the safe option quietly expires, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('be6d2982-e0a8-43e1-8122-194aad8612fe', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.97},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.77,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When the safe option quietly expires, will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and in the version no one reviews keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.72},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.74},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.97}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'When the safe option quietly expires, will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and in the version no one reviews keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1923799a-4d2d-46a7-8fd8-a81a9aa9aef5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.29},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.19,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced retail momentum chaser who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Optimizes for winning over being liked. When cornered is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; when the stakes are trivial, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.69},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.55},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.29}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'A pronounced retail momentum chaser who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Optimizes for winning over being liked. When cornered is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; when the stakes are trivial, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4b3d6e75-7996-422c-9e33-23f05de996f2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.42,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.76},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.43,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When the walls close in, weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical. Otherwise, a steady bonding-curve sniper who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and in the version no one reviews checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.58},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.63},{"slug":"status-quo","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.42,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.76}'::jsonb, 'ESFJ', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'When the walls close in, weights whatever happened most recently and vividly as if it were typical. Otherwise, a steady bonding-curve sniper who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and in the version no one reviews checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d2cfdb7c-38a5-4afc-b8f0-7b4adb7d4312', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.72,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later. Rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Once the exit narrows to one door, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.57},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later. Rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Once the exit narrows to one door, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2d311fd8-405e-45ae-ab4e-06112895c1ae', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.74,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady pairs trader: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and when no one is watching averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.53},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','outgoing']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady pairs trader: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and when no one is watching averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('918024c9-f175-406a-ab92-01fab96e4694', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.19,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Under a deadline, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","improviser"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.19,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','improviser']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Under a deadline, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b63bd2fe-a39c-463e-ab83-0efc9107b7e6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.88,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Knows the answer before it can explain the question. This prop-desk scalper chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. When the number turns red assumes the current streak is the new normal — without an audience, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Knows the answer before it can explain the question. This prop-desk scalper chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. When the number turns red assumes the current streak is the new normal — without an audience, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
