('ccd594c1-17f8-4f89-98cd-4c58414ea203', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Macro allocator, pronounced in style: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods; narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. The instant the deadline moves up underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.55},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Macro allocator, pronounced in style: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods; narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. The instant the deadline moves up underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('086403c5-7fd1-45aa-9a0f-809632f9b3cb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.1,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator, pronounced in style: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it; does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. The moment risk appears adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.72},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator, pronounced in style: narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it; does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. The moment risk appears adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a29295aa-4f94-4476-858f-5d0f53408fee', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.94,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured penny-stock gambler who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. In a pinch overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; on a slow afternoon, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.51},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A measured penny-stock gambler who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. In a pinch overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; on a slow afternoon, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.85, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('25515620-ab3c-4a9b-8a72-0a974ef6e1e1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.46,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.99,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a steady penny-stock gambler who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and on a slow afternoon backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a steady penny-stock gambler who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and on a slow afternoon backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d1539377-56ac-465d-bb36-c7332e1d1b40', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. This discretionary swing trader collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the walls close in mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — as a rule, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. This discretionary swing trader collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. When the walls close in mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — as a rule, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6aad5cd0-5186-493d-829e-1be7501ae693', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.32,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Options seller whose defining move is that they reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Confuses motion with progress. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.64},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Options seller whose defining move is that they reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Confuses motion with progress. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('08bb83e4-110a-43fd-bbc8-94f48a20056c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.25},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.24,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"In a pinch, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and when the pressure is off holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.25}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'In a pinch, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and when the pressure is off holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('45205b43-ddca-4912-95f6-ec8d1471680b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.85,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured retail momentum chaser who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Guards their energy and rations social exposure. The moment it stops being hypothetical will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one; when no one is watching, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.52},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.52},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A measured retail momentum chaser who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Guards their energy and rations social exposure. The moment it stops being hypothetical will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one; when no one is watching, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('33834c7e-8d87-4dda-b914-c2453ecf3654', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Options seller, steady in style: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved; reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Trusts momentum over preparation. When the number turns red finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Options seller, steady in style: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved; reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Trusts momentum over preparation. When the number turns red finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3f459243-e66a-4f79-940b-082d0f5cded2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.39,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This DeFi yield farmer needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. The moment risk appears delays checking the number it most needs to check — in the version no one reviews, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.59},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This DeFi yield farmer needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. The moment risk appears delays checking the number it most needs to check — in the version no one reviews, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
