('10f6f9c2-e39a-4343-8464-1c012fca9cf0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.92,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This pairs trader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When there is no clean exit gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — once the urgency drains out, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.58},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This pairs trader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When there is no clean exit gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — once the urgency drains out, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('83774b93-2d71-4ccb-9a48-1a719747b8d9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.27,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced bonding-curve sniper who narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. The moment risk appears finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; when the stakes are trivial, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.53},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'A pronounced bonding-curve sniper who narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. The moment risk appears finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; when the stakes are trivial, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5418efe3-de5f-45a2-bf7f-886214e3fc51', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.3},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.21,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"In a pinch, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and as a rule treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.6},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.3}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'In a pinch, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and as a rule treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9703112d-5d42-469c-a895-b0c7aab014fa', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.9},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.62,"alpha":0.7,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"DeFi yield farmer, pronounced in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. When there is no clean exit sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.9}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'DeFi yield farmer, pronounced in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. When there is no clean exit sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('da0612b3-2eb2-4343-8831-35790b4362b2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.89,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced perps degen who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; day to day, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced perps degen who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; day to day, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e57b4ac2-332f-4af3-a1ba-b0addcdc0a1b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.74},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. When the walls close in, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.74}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. When the walls close in, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('749878bb-06ab-4637-858a-08541b724039', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.89,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. Otherwise, a measured algorithmic market-maker who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and in the pattern nobody else tracks treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.56},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.48}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. Otherwise, a measured algorithmic market-maker who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and in the pattern nobody else tracks treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.83, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e4c87990-5c63-44fe-b5b0-9bd3f8e4c384', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.68,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.79,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This DeFi yield farmer would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. The instant it becomes irreversible takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — when the stakes are trivial, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This DeFi yield farmer would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. The instant it becomes irreversible takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — when the stakes are trivial, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2feb72ae-b077-4297-9d89-95172d873ae1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.88},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.46,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Quant researcher whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the safe option quietly expires, judges likelihood by how easily an example comes to mind, not by the base rate; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.7},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.88}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Quant researcher whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the safe option quietly expires, judges likelihood by how easily an example comes to mind, not by the base rate; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('63a03492-e07d-4ed7-b899-78f8f6f3fa7d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.88,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.32},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.63},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.36,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Under pressure, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced quant researcher who treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and once the urgency drains out trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.55},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.88,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.32}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'Under pressure, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced quant researcher who treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and once the urgency drains out trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('97eabc16-095a-40ae-be0c-af21651baa27', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.09,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Futures spreader, pronounced in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. The moment risk appears discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.52},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.48},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Futures spreader, pronounced in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. The moment risk appears discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c700f917-6401-4e9f-8119-d64fefe9de23', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.87},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.53,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This airdrop farmer reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. When the walls close in looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — in the parts nobody grades, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.74},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.87}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This airdrop farmer reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. When the walls close in looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — in the parts nobody grades, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('aac6f951-cf73-4f67-ae81-395c7fbd5fe9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.79,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced bonding-curve sniper who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and when the stakes are trivial sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced bonding-curve sniper who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and when the stakes are trivial sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8ab0f03a-572d-4852-9d51-5de7c89668f1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.79,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.39,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"The instant the deadline moves up, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and across an ordinary week holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.77},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'The instant the deadline moves up, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and across an ordinary week holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('00f7ef37-dde5-448a-ad2b-a68ca8d1d4bb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.56,"alpha":0.71,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A pronounced pairs trader: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and when the pressure is off sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.71},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.75},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A pronounced pairs trader: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and when the pressure is off sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a8d4c657-8c2e-4bc1-89e4-723a39652604', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.86,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced pairs trader who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and without an audience calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.72},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced pairs trader who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and without an audience calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('be2832ee-6b61-4165-ae57-1b217e4a3367', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.7,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. This penny-stock gambler chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and maintains flawless records nobody asked for. When cornered is more certain than the hit rate justifies — in the small things, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.53},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. This penny-stock gambler chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and maintains flawless records nobody asked for. When cornered is more certain than the hit rate justifies — in the small things, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('728f19b5-19db-43ce-8b07-e0ea646a9ea8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.72},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.57,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady retail momentum chaser who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. When the walls close in guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains; in the parts nobody grades, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.72}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A steady retail momentum chaser who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. When the walls close in guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains; in the parts nobody grades, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.86, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('80edc094-faa1-40ce-ad76-f6af8bc2a737', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When cornered, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced DeFi yield farmer who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and on an ordinary week rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.53},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'When cornered, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced DeFi yield farmer who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and on an ordinary week rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('cfcd08ad-1e20-4079-a688-168fe77ca2e0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.8,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. This pairs trader reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. The instant it becomes irreversible cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — across an ordinary week, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. This pairs trader reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. The instant it becomes irreversible cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — across an ordinary week, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('faf63d82-7767-42e3-8f56-0de1add3c461', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.86,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.81,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and as a rule trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and as a rule trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('39817fbb-d0a0-4e40-af0b-8cf8a3b3d58d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.75},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.45,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. This commodities speculator notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Once the exit narrows to one door looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — when the pressure is off, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.56},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.55},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.75}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. This commodities speculator notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Once the exit narrows to one door looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — when the pressure is off, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.89, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('01a3d438-e943-4c80-8e95-a8f81d5625bb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.34,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.32},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.51,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.21,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. Otherwise, a pronounced discretionary swing trader who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and in the small things confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.57},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.34,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.32}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. Otherwise, a pronounced discretionary swing trader who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and in the small things confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6530372b-2e48-430e-b969-9ab50a230422', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.9,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. The instant it becomes irreversible, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. The instant it becomes irreversible, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0d64e39a-aedc-4dff-ba15-fd2c1c733eb6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.95,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Pairs trader, measured in style: measures decisions by who they might upset. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Once things get tense abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.47},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Pairs trader, measured in style: measures decisions by who they might upset. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Once things get tense abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.88, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4e174cde-66e6-4978-b028-94ffd445a678', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.03,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker, steady in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. In a pinch abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker, steady in style: defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely; plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. In a pinch abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.83, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('95df422a-9638-4eff-b814-346f662b54d5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.86,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts momentum over preparation. This crypto day-trader reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When there is no clean exit treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — when the pressure is off, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.55},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Trusts momentum over preparation. This crypto day-trader reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When there is no clean exit treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — when the pressure is off, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d3b07855-c027-4aa8-bf3a-2140f0ddff2a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.19},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.22,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When someone is watching the outcome, expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and on an ordinary week treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.54},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.66},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.19}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making']::text[], 'When someone is watching the outcome, expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and on an ordinary week treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('62903a14-507a-4b41-af78-14d94cde5383', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.45,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.7},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.55,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense. A steady pairs trader: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and when no one is watching talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.45,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.7}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense. A steady pairs trader: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and when no one is watching talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.89, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('194b4a2d-c5e7-4b9c-9bd7-bf90c1ee7c4b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.72,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.84,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the walls close in, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a steady perps degen who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and measures decisions by who they might upset. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and in the small things names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.48},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.52},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.48}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.72,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'When the walls close in, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a steady perps degen who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and measures decisions by who they might upset. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and in the small things names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.88, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c95c54b0-e9b1-4d17-a49f-0688e829c189', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.29,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced volatility arbitrageur: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and on a slow afternoon checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced volatility arbitrageur: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and on a slow afternoon checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b8436dee-995d-4df5-8782-48a0b84b56a5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.7},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.76,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Zero-DTE options gambler, pronounced in style: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. When there is no clean exit discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.7}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing']::text[], 'Zero-DTE options gambler, pronounced in style: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. When there is no clean exit discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('da860e31-e9a1-434d-a5f8-bfb6431eb503', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.76},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.42,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This discretionary swing trader reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line judges likelihood by how easily an example comes to mind, not by the base rate — without an audience, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.57},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.58},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.76}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This discretionary swing trader reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line judges likelihood by how easily an example comes to mind, not by the base rate — without an audience, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1a8cea5f-a2d8-4346-b790-445df163da80', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.05},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.79,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.75},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.27,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Macro allocator, pronounced in style: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation; assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Under pressure is more certain than the hit rate justifies.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.8},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.69},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.05}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making']::text[], 'Macro allocator, pronounced in style: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation; assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Under pressure is more certain than the hit rate justifies.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c8878a17-0c3a-4e7c-ae66-05e6ab748b15', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.07,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant the deadline moves up, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced bonding-curve sniper who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and optimizes for winning over being liked. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and across the quiet stretches sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'The instant the deadline moves up, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced bonding-curve sniper who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and optimizes for winning over being liked. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and across the quiet stretches sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('86353249-8b5f-49f7-9d3d-b077ef172316', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.67,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.29,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A steady discretionary swing trader who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. When the stakes rise cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; across an ordinary week, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A steady discretionary swing trader who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. When the stakes rise cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; across an ordinary week, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('38117e8b-e703-4919-8a62-481aa52e87a4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.8,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A measured penny-stock gambler: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and as a rule treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.49},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.55},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.52},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A measured penny-stock gambler: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it, and as a rule treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.88, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bd5e9de6-8a6f-4d8d-9745-385177b7507f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.84,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced futures spreader who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Under a deadline mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; in the version no one reviews, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced futures spreader who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Under a deadline mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; in the version no one reviews, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d541f3a0-2e08-4c5a-b602-ae5b288ed28c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the stakes rise, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a pronounced DeFi yield farmer who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and in the unglamorous middle of things rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.63},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a pronounced DeFi yield farmer who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and in the unglamorous middle of things rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bbc8e8d7-5fd9-4f52-83e4-2f951d412335', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.85},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.6,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When cornered, guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and when the stakes are trivial keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.67},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.61},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.69},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.85}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'When cornered, guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and when the stakes are trivial keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('37a0f80c-2bb6-4972-83a9-391a04986580', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.72,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.07,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Options seller, steady in style: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation; notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Once the exit narrows to one door would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.54},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.52},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.5},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.72,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Options seller, steady in style: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation; notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Once the exit narrows to one door would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('148b0c3b-d107-427a-b189-024d31d8e6ea', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.67,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and on an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.63},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.54},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.53},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and on an ordinary week sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('add8245b-234a-40b1-a50b-d04cb5f651ee', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.92},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.66,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Value investor, pronounced in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. The moment risk appears guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.76},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.74},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.92}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Value investor, pronounced in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. The moment risk appears guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9fb6a05e-2e6c-498d-96a0-a5c87327a826', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.95,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This macro allocator gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When the walls close in extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — day to day, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This macro allocator gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When the walls close in extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — day to day, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('293fa221-d6e0-4bd5-8df7-9f954c22402e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.32},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.47,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.29,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Quant researcher, pronounced in style: cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. When someone is watching the outcome rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.56},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.66},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.32}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making']::text[], 'Quant researcher, pronounced in style: cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete; would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. When someone is watching the outcome rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('56866389-d4d6-4923-9090-4504cc830210', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.82,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The moment it stops being hypothetical, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. Otherwise, a pronounced prop-desk scalper who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error, and in the small things refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'The moment it stops being hypothetical, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. Otherwise, a pronounced prop-desk scalper who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error, and in the small things refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7322c190-df2c-43fc-bf42-088768fe458a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.73,"narcissism":0.86,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced pairs trader who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Under a deadline is more certain than the hit rate justifies; when the stakes are trivial, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced pairs trader who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Under a deadline is more certain than the hit rate justifies; when the stakes are trivial, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
