('d56d8f26-8c94-4624-aaca-39daffcd4dd6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.47,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Bonding-curve sniper, steady in style: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. When cornered jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.57},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Bonding-curve sniper, steady in style: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. When cornered jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e50d8aa1-ca2e-42b2-a8bf-a243c9668000', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.78,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.32,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. A pronounced airdrop farmer: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and left to their own devices trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.61},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'Underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. A pronounced airdrop farmer: front-loads the work and double-checks it twice, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and left to their own devices trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3b7622a0-b16f-44bc-bc48-c2241da0792e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.72},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.44,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.63,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A steady macro allocator: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and in the routine of it holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.72}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A steady macro allocator: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence, recharges by being around people, not away from them. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and in the routine of it holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b04fbb36-7688-4abf-bb94-0977e039b3b7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.45,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced crypto day-trader who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. When cornered feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused; in the pattern nobody else tracks, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A pronounced crypto day-trader who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. When cornered feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused; in the pattern nobody else tracks, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('98614869-4970-4c94-9754-0de7e119e0b6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.84,"narcissism":0.52,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.45,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When someone is watching the outcome, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.63},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When someone is watching the outcome, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('af4ec1fa-3959-4e18-9d93-20d8a161ecd0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.95,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Value investor, pronounced in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Under a deadline assumes the current streak is the new normal.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Value investor, pronounced in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Under a deadline assumes the current streak is the new normal.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('21532b7a-1319-4271-9481-4f9bba7a81bc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.05,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured meme-coin rotator who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. The moment risk appears would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for; when the stakes are trivial, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.5},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A measured meme-coin rotator who would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. The moment risk appears would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for; when the stakes are trivial, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.84, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('34024d5e-2576-42d7-98b5-6f6025d15028', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.37,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, optimizes for winning over being liked. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and in the routine of it confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.46},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.54},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades, optimizes for winning over being liked. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and in the routine of it confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3dfe61cd-4035-4b5d-bf11-0f6be5eb855f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.48,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.26,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Lets the deadline make the decision by default. This MEV searcher needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line judges likelihood by how easily an example comes to mind, not by the base rate — once the urgency drains out, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.57},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.48,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Lets the deadline make the decision by default. This MEV searcher needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one and treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line judges likelihood by how easily an example comes to mind, not by the base rate — once the urgency drains out, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ff7d4ef3-be14-4e7c-8139-161e1d6413c5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.67,"narcissism":0.85,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.75,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced perps degen: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and across the quiet stretches holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. A pronounced perps degen: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and across the quiet stretches holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('966a8dff-f6d8-4fce-bfc8-05251afa301b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced MEV searcher: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and without an audience treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing']::text[], 'Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced MEV searcher: thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision, gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and without an audience treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('891a748d-4033-40d9-b7cf-a3c3efd62ebe', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.33,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A steady macro allocator: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and in the pattern nobody else tracks treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.67},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.68},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A steady macro allocator: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and in the pattern nobody else tracks treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('56343870-f972-4f60-8f8a-fb88a933f53b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.88},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.66,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced commodities speculator who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. The instant it becomes irreversible feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; in the routine of it, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.88}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced commodities speculator who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. The instant it becomes irreversible feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; in the routine of it, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('447ba3be-2398-4f8c-90b3-351d4c5002b2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.79,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur whose defining move is that they would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.59},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.63},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.63},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.76,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur whose defining move is that they would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. Over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('070faeb7-16d6-4d90-8f03-ebd8b738b0a5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.11,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. This value investor chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When there is no clean exit underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong — in the unglamorous middle of things, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.6},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.48},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.54},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. This value investor chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When there is no clean exit underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong — in the unglamorous middle of things, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('fecba2cd-356a-414d-87e4-1ddb0cc2c44a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.69,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady index-fund holdout who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. The moment risk appears would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; on a slow afternoon, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.63},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A steady index-fund holdout who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. The moment risk appears would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; on a slow afternoon, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('79a60998-abba-40e9-9d64-411312fc47c6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.33,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Pairs trader whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. The instant it becomes irreversible, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Pairs trader whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. The instant it becomes irreversible, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('234cdd0b-ccf5-4a59-901a-230c7c451f63', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.69},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.32,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.08,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Once things get tense, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.74},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.75,"neuroticism":0.69}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Once things get tense, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2a315b3f-387c-46ca-84ba-71e0fd578706', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.72},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.47,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady DeFi yield farmer who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. The moment risk appears overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; in the small things, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.65},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.57},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.72}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A steady DeFi yield farmer who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. The moment risk appears overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; in the small things, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('668c0f66-c38e-4cdc-b9b0-72c79cea16ae', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.77,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the downside gets concrete, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. Otherwise, a steady volatility arbitrageur who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and when the stakes are trivial apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'When the downside gets concrete, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. Otherwise, a steady volatility arbitrageur who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and when the stakes are trivial apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a387b532-3e16-4801-b65d-ca8e70c5e11f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.79,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts momentum over preparation. This pairs trader gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. When the number turns red discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — when no one is watching, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Trusts momentum over preparation. This pairs trader gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. When the number turns red discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — when no one is watching, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3a3ac3bd-613e-43a6-b8c7-92beea0df434', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This macro allocator reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. The instant the deadline moves up assumes the current streak is the new normal — in the routine of it, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This macro allocator reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. The instant the deadline moves up assumes the current streak is the new normal — in the routine of it, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ece218eb-6fa9-4e2f-8ccb-40a2947e61a8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.89,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a steady crypto day-trader who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and left to their own devices treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.48},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.56},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a steady crypto day-trader who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete and takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and left to their own devices treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.84, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('456d8ca3-b236-4537-8e79-62b2f56c4505', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.76},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.18,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. The moment risk appears, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.72},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.92,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.76}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser whose defining move is that they narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. The moment risk appears, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d0b03542-4998-4fac-be33-635a32bd7a9a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.52,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.65,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Confuses motion with progress. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Confuses motion with progress. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c29023cf-30cb-4230-821b-61de5164e881', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.89},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.58,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Once things get tense looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; without an audience, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.76},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.81}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.89}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Once things get tense looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; without an audience, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('907fde75-d710-4272-a36d-82d3dada5b2c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.02,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Options seller, measured in style: measures decisions by who they might upset. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. The moment risk appears defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.53},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.51},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.48},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Options seller, measured in style: measures decisions by who they might upset. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. The moment risk appears defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence.', 0.82, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0732b171-9f1b-4dae-adbf-02d4b1265372', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.95,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced DeFi yield farmer who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. The instant the deadline moves up abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; in the pattern nobody else tracks, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.81},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.75},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'A pronounced DeFi yield farmer who thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. The instant the deadline moves up abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; in the pattern nobody else tracks, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a64953dc-9f2b-43d8-a555-0a0537d299a3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.14,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.96},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. This dividend-yield chaser gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — when no one is watching, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.54},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. This dividend-yield chaser gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend — when no one is watching, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ae02b713-1b71-4b2b-8ec9-21b18b05ebc6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.8,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains. A steady liquidation-bot operator: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the routine of it trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.51},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.51},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains. A steady liquidation-bot operator: takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the routine of it trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.83, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ccd7c1d4-592d-424b-800a-7048d4278c1c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.02,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Keeps paying into something mainly because of what has already been paid. A steady delta-neutral market maker: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and without an audience sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.58},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.54},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Keeps paying into something mainly because of what has already been paid. A steady delta-neutral market maker: would rather lose a point than win an argument badly, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and without an audience sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ee90150a-e6cf-400b-81fa-68ef0aac29f4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.39},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.28,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Options seller, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line is more certain than the hit rate justifies.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.56},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.39}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Options seller, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line is more certain than the hit rate justifies.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9fc535ec-5c32-4b6f-acf6-2feafa52205c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.89},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.25,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.38,"alpha":0.72,"beta":0.74},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Airdrop farmer, pronounced in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Under pressure looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.66},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.65},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.89}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Airdrop farmer, pronounced in style: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Under pressure looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0688e939-0ecc-48ae-a63f-ab656bc00e0e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.15,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This volatility arbitrageur reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Under pressure finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — across an ordinary week, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.58},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This volatility arbitrageur reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Under pressure finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees — across an ordinary week, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1f3c61e7-f5c1-47c0-a6f5-36cda6e9a9bc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.68,"narcissism":0.87,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.8,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Once the exit narrows to one door takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.21,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Once the exit narrows to one door takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bb0e36e2-0d51-44a8-b6d9-09838482ec7c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.08,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady penny-stock gambler: recharges by being around people, not away from them, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and day to day treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady penny-stock gambler: recharges by being around people, not away from them, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and day to day treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d7ea29b9-e8d3-4a9d-8922-c5137c41b17f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.2,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.87,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.91,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When the downside gets concrete, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.57},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.2,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When the downside gets concrete, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('cf806024-afbb-420e-abff-6640124d26b3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.74,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the stakes rise, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced perps degen who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet, and across an ordinary week averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced perps degen who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet, and across an ordinary week averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6c9b45da-3a5e-4e0e-a70e-c612a5d9e92e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.88},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.68,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This volatility arbitrageur hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. The moment risk appears feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly — across the quiet stretches, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.61,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.88}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This volatility arbitrageur hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. The moment risk appears feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly — across the quiet stretches, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('46d7653e-679a-4cfc-b22b-6436daafb4f2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.75},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.56,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady dividend-yield chaser who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. The moment it stops being hypothetical guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains; in the small things, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.57},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.63},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.75}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A steady dividend-yield chaser who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. The moment it stops being hypothetical guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains; in the small things, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('67115c45-0c3d-4cb0-9ef5-a5718b1b96d3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.1,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and in the small things trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.53},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A pronounced dividend-yield chaser: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and in the small things trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6bd8cc47-6d67-4bdc-aa06-d6f2db3469dc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.3},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.86,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.27,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. When there is no clean exit, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.56},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.71},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.3}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader whose defining move is that they front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. When there is no clean exit, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b5766a29-3d75-4944-8839-53a256ceadba', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.37},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.5,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.2,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. This value investor over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Once the exit narrows to one door remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along — without an audience, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.64},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.37}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. This value investor over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Once the exit narrows to one door remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along — without an audience, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('26b6b2ab-2760-45b4-981b-4fd5901c4a86', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.2},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.33,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When the walls close in holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; on a slow afternoon, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.67},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.71},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.2}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When the walls close in holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; on a slow afternoon, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
