('4da2f3cb-006c-4a36-a7cc-3da5436e9abb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.74,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader, pronounced in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. When the number turns red treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader, pronounced in style: chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades; needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. When the number turns red treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('63d782ba-07fe-4486-8f6c-38ab040acc3b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.14,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Quant researcher whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Once the exit narrows to one door, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.56},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Quant researcher whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Once the exit narrows to one door, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('46d10dc2-6d01-4fba-9724-84c1b2680f09', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.74},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.16,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. This penny-stock gambler treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. In a pinch treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — without an audience, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.78},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.74}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. This penny-stock gambler treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. In a pinch treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — without an audience, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e6ff8cc1-3487-4588-8006-e3e5f5a48c54', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.21},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.79,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.64},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.31,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced prop-desk scalper who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. The moment it stops being hypothetical holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; on a slow afternoon, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.67},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.21}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'A pronounced prop-desk scalper who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. The moment it stops being hypothetical holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support; on a slow afternoon, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4732a0c0-3d7a-4e9e-9c1f-236bd49f4e73', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.72},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady meme-coin rotator: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and across the quiet stretches names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.72}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady meme-coin rotator: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and across the quiet stretches names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f619f35e-1311-4ba5-815e-71ba38c3b150', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.77,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced airdrop farmer who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the safe option quietly expires cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; when no one is watching, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced airdrop farmer who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the safe option quietly expires cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; when no one is watching, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2056aeaa-f358-435c-9a9e-1f0e748348e7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.23},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.69},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.29,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns, treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and when the stakes are trivial sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.73},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.23}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns, treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and when the stakes are trivial sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('abbc976f-05fe-410b-8629-f5c69b24118e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.71},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.99,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced DeFi yield farmer who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Once the exit narrows to one door jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; when the stakes are trivial, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.71}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'A pronounced DeFi yield farmer who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Once the exit narrows to one door jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; when the stakes are trivial, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9c96f262-e615-4195-8509-7fec4f516453', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.02,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"In a pinch, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady penny-stock gambler who recharges by being around people, not away from them and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and left to their own devices keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'In a pinch, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady penny-stock gambler who recharges by being around people, not away from them and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and left to their own devices keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0fb3136f-0fad-420d-b91e-c0857c3ab5da', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.85,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and in the parts nobody grades rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.63},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.55},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.51},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains. Otherwise, a steady airdrop farmer who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and in the parts nobody grades rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0ec09a8d-f958-44a6-b230-f263357819a2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.5,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.89,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady meme-coin rotator who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. The instant the deadline moves up would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for; day to day, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.55},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.52},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A steady meme-coin rotator who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. The instant the deadline moves up would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for; day to day, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4a46ffae-b193-4a53-b53f-6ba0619d7209', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.53,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady algorithmic market-maker: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and across the quiet stretches screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady algorithmic market-maker: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and across the quiet stretches screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c8a5b288-c9e0-4374-bdf4-a73eb917f0f6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.92,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the downside gets concrete, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced penny-stock gambler who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and optimizes for winning over being liked. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later, and when the pressure is off keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.53},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'When the downside gets concrete, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced penny-stock gambler who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and optimizes for winning over being liked. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later, and when the pressure is off keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3f78614a-1952-4eda-b059-878f5b530207', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.15,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Options seller, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. When cornered assumes the current streak is the new normal.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Options seller, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; recharges by being around people, not away from them. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. When cornered assumes the current streak is the new normal.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('cc18538b-0840-40c1-92ac-ae6baeed7a5f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.69,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Retail momentum chaser, pronounced in style: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject; treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Once the exit narrows to one door extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Retail momentum chaser, pronounced in style: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject; treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. Once the exit narrows to one door extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8fda256e-bad2-444d-a336-1b271c290c26', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.94,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. A steady bonding-curve sniper: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it, maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the pattern nobody else tracks confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for. A steady bonding-curve sniper: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it, maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the pattern nobody else tracks confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.86, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('45c62375-47cf-4f06-aa9d-bdc4dc3c6075', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.76,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A pronounced volatility arbitrageur: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and once the urgency drains out confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.25,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A pronounced volatility arbitrageur: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and once the urgency drains out confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('821971c3-126e-4fde-a194-6386dc55f56f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.84,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs. Otherwise, a measured discretionary swing trader who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the small things keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.47},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.49},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.57},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.5}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs. Otherwise, a measured discretionary swing trader who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and in the small things keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.8, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('356c3e62-8964-4a05-9f3f-06b142bfbcc4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Perps degen, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. In a pinch extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Perps degen, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. In a pinch extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4c4e5b98-d9c3-488e-b084-f9fd32f20bcd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.44,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.72},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.45,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A steady discretionary swing trader: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and without an audience names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.6},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.44,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.72}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis. A steady discretionary swing trader: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and without an audience names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
