('fea27733-c8de-4ed0-8c0a-107aeea5d3a8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Retail momentum chaser whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Retail momentum chaser whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bd72bb5e-d225-4802-bc21-e5b248275af6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.7},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.97,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Bonding-curve sniper whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. When the downside gets concrete, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.7}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Bonding-curve sniper whose defining move is that they draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. When the downside gets concrete, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('52826b8c-661f-4f8d-b8ad-6d5d41d1a2d2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.03,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Crypto day-trader, steady in style: maintains flawless records nobody asked for; would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.5},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.55},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.52},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader, steady in style: maintains flawless records nobody asked for; would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains.', 0.83, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bae67bd6-fe52-4d3f-b374-3625b7ae41e4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.81,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.22},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.86,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.36,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Zero-DTE options gambler, steady in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; optimizes for winning over being liked. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. When cornered holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","open-minded","temperament"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.81,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.22}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','open-minded','temperament']::text[], 'Zero-DTE options gambler, steady in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; optimizes for winning over being liked. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. When cornered holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d9c10844-38df-4386-afc8-7f9c58383138', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.79,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"MEV searcher whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Optimizes for winning over being liked. The instant it becomes irreversible, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'MEV searcher whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Optimizes for winning over being liked. The instant it becomes irreversible, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery; exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7aef08a5-7153-4223-bbe8-3d335b0466d7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.93,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured dividend-yield chaser who measures decisions by who they might upset. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When someone is watching the outcome assumes the current streak is the new normal; in the version no one reviews, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.54},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.5},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A measured dividend-yield chaser who measures decisions by who they might upset. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When someone is watching the outcome assumes the current streak is the new normal; in the version no one reviews, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.81, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('51840304-9c10-4bd5-86cd-86c48b3686f2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.26,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.57,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, is swayed by which number comes first, not just what the numbers mean. Otherwise, a steady onchain copy-trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and confuses motion with progress. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and on a slow afternoon treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.63},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.68},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, is swayed by which number comes first, not just what the numbers mean. Otherwise, a steady onchain copy-trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and confuses motion with progress. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and on a slow afternoon treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c81d2951-cc57-4585-8dbc-5faf2053c45c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.21,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When the safe option quietly expires, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a steady options seller who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and as a rule keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'When the safe option quietly expires, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a steady options seller who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and as a rule keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
