('8be49cc4-7f3e-4984-a9c0-d6c9d8457aad', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.12,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady quant researcher who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Trusts momentum over preparation. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the downside gets concrete discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; on an ordinary week, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.72},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'A steady quant researcher who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Trusts momentum over preparation. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the downside gets concrete discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; on an ordinary week, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c5ee41d6-bed7-4462-a873-6d8773a73245', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.37,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.29},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.2,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When someone is watching the outcome rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact; across the quiet stretches, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.62},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.37,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.29}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. When someone is watching the outcome rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact; across the quiet stretches, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5691afd5-70db-4b9a-b393-aeae488ef5ac', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.73,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Zero-DTE options gambler, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. When the number turns red extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Zero-DTE options gambler, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Knows the answer before it can explain the question. When the number turns red extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('23d957ef-d63d-4aba-9b00-ea11e93c1843', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.42,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.87},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.36,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur, pronounced in style: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one; defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.7},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.42,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.87}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur, pronounced in style: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one; defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bb0a6962-40a6-41b8-8523-048764ffd819', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.14,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced index-fund holdout who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the safe option quietly expires assumes the current streak is the new normal; in the unglamorous middle of things, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.46,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced index-fund holdout who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the safe option quietly expires assumes the current streak is the new normal; in the unglamorous middle of things, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ac8cb56f-1576-4ec9-bd9e-d17c46e1f7fc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.36},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.05,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and on a slow afternoon checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.5},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.36}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and on a slow afternoon checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c56e03c2-e8ba-4ba4-8ff1-bfbd91b2acc0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.61,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.02,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady value investor who starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Once the exit narrows to one door is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; day to day, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.78},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","improviser"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','improviser']::text[], 'A steady value investor who starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Once the exit narrows to one door is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest; day to day, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ba2fd161-a3aa-4deb-9bb9-14d49dfda873', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.82,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.26,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A steady bonding-curve sniper who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Under a deadline underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; when the stakes are trivial, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","open-minded","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.82,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','open-minded','ipip-neo']::text[], 'A steady bonding-curve sniper who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Under a deadline underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; when the stakes are trivial, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0b294ef5-ffb2-419b-840a-60ffdaca1d43', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.81,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady penny-stock gambler who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. When there is no clean exit adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; in the version no one reviews, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.59},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.56},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A steady penny-stock gambler who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. When there is no clean exit adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has; in the version no one reviews, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('74c139c4-763c-405a-8111-ba69176f6f2f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.88},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.75,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.73},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A pronounced options seller: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and when the pressure is off apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.75},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.88}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A pronounced options seller: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and when the pressure is off apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bc90fa3b-3781-46dd-8420-516c97efeff8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.73,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When the walls close in extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; across the quiet stretches, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. When the walls close in extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; across the quiet stretches, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7d17cefa-3d1f-4b82-b1bd-8debe8d65cee', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.74,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. Otherwise, a pronounced prop-desk scalper who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly, and once the urgency drains out keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.55},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.74},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. Otherwise, a pronounced prop-desk scalper who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly, and once the urgency drains out keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a5a8190d-1b93-4f80-addd-c355607e8572', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.65,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Airdrop farmer, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. The instant it becomes irreversible would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.71},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Airdrop farmer, steady in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. The instant it becomes irreversible would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5b6b3331-e5b0-44d0-806f-a32ac2058bd2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.57,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Perps degen, pronounced in style: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence; defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. When someone is watching the outcome feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Perps degen, pronounced in style: spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence; defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. When someone is watching the outcome feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('fdced97b-b5a7-4012-b4fc-625a2d4f6475', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.49,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced index-fund holdout who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When cornered feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused; in the unglamorous middle of things, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.65},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A pronounced index-fund holdout who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When cornered feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused; in the unglamorous middle of things, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8cb0525f-b987-45b0-8b2a-5b74172e0e9a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.18,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. The instant it becomes irreversible, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.54},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. The instant it becomes irreversible, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2e1d9acb-126a-46db-af80-a78ef703d657', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.68},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.88,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"In a pinch, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced index-fund holdout who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and on a slow afternoon treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.68}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'In a pinch, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. Otherwise, a pronounced index-fund holdout who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Knows the answer before it can explain the question, and on a slow afternoon treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('683933a9-f093-4e93-a3af-458bfde70d82', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.57,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains. A pronounced discretionary swing trader: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and as a rule checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains. A pronounced discretionary swing trader: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and as a rule checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a8a5683c-9311-47b5-b355-3e7a1479198e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.93,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured crypto day-trader who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Once things get tense gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns; day to day, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.54},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.48}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A measured crypto day-trader who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Once things get tense gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns; day to day, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.85, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('be644033-d06c-4408-b932-19331ca5246f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.79,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A pronounced options seller: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error, and when the pressure is off backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A pronounced options seller: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error, and when the pressure is off backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a9c65c11-6db7-4ada-8a7e-bb92d06dc863', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.22,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. When the safe option quietly expires, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. When the safe option quietly expires, takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4e32d22e-3484-4cf5-9f76-6f3ec2286d14', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.81,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.23},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.84,"narcissism":0.53,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.22,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Airdrop farmer, pronounced in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. The moment risk appears assumes the bad statistic applies to other people.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.57},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","open-minded","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.81,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.23}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','open-minded','risk']::text[], 'Airdrop farmer, pronounced in style: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working; maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. The moment risk appears assumes the bad statistic applies to other people.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f0c59ae6-a54a-4280-a88f-68abffff5d8f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.97},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.2,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.71,"alpha":0.7,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and when the stakes are trivial sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.76},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.77},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.76},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.97}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and when the stakes are trivial sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7cecb62f-5260-469c-9596-0b9589204dbb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.69},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.94,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A steady discretionary swing trader: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and in the parts nobody grades trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.69}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A steady discretionary swing trader: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and in the parts nobody grades trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('18c8d617-5b9a-43bd-a310-385b71af984e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.47,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.73,"alpha":0.72,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When the walls close in, sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and on a slow afternoon sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.65},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'When the walls close in, sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and on a slow afternoon sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5ce1f879-1b80-4b18-abc7-6f70f24e20a9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.88},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.66,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Pairs trader whose defining move is that they notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Once things get tense, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.75},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.76},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.88}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Pairs trader whose defining move is that they notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. Reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Once things get tense, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('66bee8dc-6041-42c2-a9e3-8390db4c95dd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.8},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.62,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady index-fund holdout: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and left to their own devices keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.8}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A steady index-fund holdout: rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen, improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and left to their own devices keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('183f8dd3-261d-4189-ab21-10ff1181b3f8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.98,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur, steady in style: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault; cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When the safe option quietly expires would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.55},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.56},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.48}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur, steady in style: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault; cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. When the safe option quietly expires would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for.', 0.84, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('53bca98d-b22d-4a50-85d2-cb6a28f413ef', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.18,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced retail momentum chaser who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. In a pinch assumes the current streak is the new normal; on a slow afternoon, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.53},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced retail momentum chaser who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. In a pinch assumes the current streak is the new normal; on a slow afternoon, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0aea2e9d-cc02-4f97-8788-e31f95a54c28', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.93,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.78,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced perps degen: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error, and in the unglamorous middle of things sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.74},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. A pronounced perps degen: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Treats overthinking as its own kind of error, and in the unglamorous middle of things sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
