('8ad0f198-35f4-4240-ab2b-b14bdb95e7db', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.14,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.7,"narcissism":0.87,"psychopathy":0.71},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.89,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This options seller reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When the number turns red discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — in the routine of it, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.14,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly. This options seller reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When the number turns red discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — in the routine of it, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c5dffa57-920c-4cf5-b366-f37c5b80fa85', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced meme-coin rotator who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. Once things get tense finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; in the small things, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced meme-coin rotator who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. Once things get tense finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; in the small things, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1eefa707-19ea-4b73-a317-587e12df8318', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.17},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.17,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Macro allocator whose defining move is that they builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. The instant the deadline moves up, is more certain than the hit rate justifies; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.67},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.17}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'Macro allocator whose defining move is that they builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. The instant the deadline moves up, is more certain than the hit rate justifies; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f0ddd6bb-fd0f-462a-a2ad-18b179a5e70c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.69},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.97,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Bonding-curve sniper, pronounced in style: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved; takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.74},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.69}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Bonding-curve sniper, pronounced in style: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved; takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c3e53b92-e514-4ab0-93d0-0b7a353dbd9b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.29,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced quant researcher who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. The instant the deadline moves up assumes the current streak is the new normal; once the urgency drains out, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.57},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced quant researcher who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. The instant the deadline moves up assumes the current streak is the new normal; once the urgency drains out, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1fc8727f-cdcb-4ac8-98a6-afb7c3ab4239', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.68,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. The instant it becomes irreversible, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. The instant it becomes irreversible, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6a41a69c-2de6-45df-9c60-a74a32304f6c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.89,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Pairs trader, steady in style: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. When the stakes rise feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.48},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.68,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Pairs trader, steady in style: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. When the stakes rise feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains.', 0.84, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4515cb25-fa60-4930-857b-6604f0f8fbde', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.21,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.67,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This macro allocator hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — as a rule, averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.21,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This macro allocator hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap — as a rule, averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('125e4743-74f2-403f-8b03-fee15213d249', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.21,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Once the exit narrows to one door, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Once the exit narrows to one door, extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('51708589-10ae-414a-9184-1ae755953751', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.37,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced retail momentum chaser who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the number turns red expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately; as a rule, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.38,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced retail momentum chaser who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the number turns red expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately; as a rule, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e37f6709-e8e8-4269-97a3-caca908d364e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.87,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.77,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. This airdrop farmer reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. The instant it becomes irreversible assumes the current streak is the new normal — across an ordinary week, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. This airdrop farmer reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. The instant it becomes irreversible assumes the current streak is the new normal — across an ordinary week, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b2d2380a-6bc9-4f4e-a6e5-9c85bc150296', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.15,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. A steady macro allocator: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and in the unglamorous middle of things holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. A steady macro allocator: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject, leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and in the unglamorous middle of things holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c51180ae-0905-4ada-910e-3f1a8a548351', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.05,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When the downside gets concrete, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.54},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.55},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When the downside gets concrete, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('fee9dfa8-41f7-49d7-af88-3b1b2deb8e0c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.49,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.77,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady prop-desk scalper who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. When the downside gets concrete rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact; when the stakes are trivial, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.5},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.49}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A steady prop-desk scalper who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. When the downside gets concrete rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact; when the stakes are trivial, holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b6ef6d08-9918-4da7-b855-6e53aea0fabd', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.45,"alpha":0.7,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and as a rule screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.72},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.74}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.52,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced liquidation-bot operator: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting, and as a rule screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1618a87c-f640-4dc6-981f-1bc03f9138e6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.88,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. This penny-stock gambler gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When the stakes rise cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — left to their own devices, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. This penny-stock gambler gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and would rather be respected than liked, and says so. When the stakes rise cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — left to their own devices, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d9bb9f86-a1f2-4126-9a07-d547984cd303', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.15},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.86,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.75},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.43,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced algorithmic market-maker who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do. When someone is watching the outcome underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; on a slow afternoon, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.5},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.87},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.72},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","open-minded","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.15}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','open-minded','behavioral']::text[], 'A pronounced algorithmic market-maker who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do. When someone is watching the outcome underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; on a slow afternoon, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6ca73642-7f11-437d-aa68-244fd572b166', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.75,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A steady airdrop farmer: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and left to their own devices keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A steady airdrop farmer: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and left to their own devices keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('15585b18-6260-4c37-b9e9-f02e9441f8cc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.67,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady prop-desk scalper who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Under a deadline looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; on an ordinary week, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.76},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A steady prop-desk scalper who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Under a deadline looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; on an ordinary week, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('98bb5367-f776-41b3-b71f-8be40191f099', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.46,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.26,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. This MEV searcher would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Once the exit narrows to one door assumes the current streak is the new normal — in the parts nobody grades, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.46,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. This MEV searcher would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Once the exit narrows to one door assumes the current streak is the new normal — in the parts nobody grades, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e556aefe-903a-4c69-ab29-3f3194e206bf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.33},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.22,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Once things get tense, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and in the pattern nobody else tracks trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.33}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'Once things get tense, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and in the pattern nobody else tracks trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0f65e85b-0d0d-4d4f-b781-70101cd61a5e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.44,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.41,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision; treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. The instant the deadline moves up would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.63},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.59},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.62},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.44,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision; treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. The instant the deadline moves up would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.', 0.86, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3fb20413-d45d-4fd1-b475-ad7668252085', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.39},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.18,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Volatility arbitrageur, pronounced in style: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. The moment it stops being hypothetical holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.64},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.39}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'Volatility arbitrageur, pronounced in style: builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work; collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. The moment it stops being hypothetical holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ea2f3d61-5fd0-420b-8244-7c59c27fbe7d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.95,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced crypto day-trader who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When cornered treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; when no one is watching, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced crypto day-trader who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When cornered treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; when no one is watching, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('af7f535a-5cad-469f-921f-b42fa97e4a3c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.78,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced meme-coin rotator: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and once the urgency drains out screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced meme-coin rotator: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and once the urgency drains out screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6e5979ec-5da4-4416-a11c-ec6f8c5a9128', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.63},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.7,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Crypto day-trader, pronounced in style: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system; treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. When there is no clean exit extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.63}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader, pronounced in style: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system; treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. When there is no clean exit extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('aa7f8074-22cc-475b-af7f-2c5c73fd1c4c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.2,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Macro allocator, pronounced in style: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. The instant it becomes irreversible finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.57},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Macro allocator, pronounced in style: reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject; thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. The instant it becomes irreversible finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('543ba46d-c18a-4d24-867d-8059ba0bc6a2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.27},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.94,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady onchain copy-trader who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Once things get tense abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; as a rule, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'A steady onchain copy-trader who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Once things get tense abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; as a rule, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('982356a7-3c70-481b-84ba-9880aaef40be', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.89,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Trusts momentum over preparation. This zero-DTE options gambler reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and recharges by being around people, not away from them. When the walls close in assumes the current streak is the new normal — in the pattern nobody else tracks, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Trusts momentum over preparation. This zero-DTE options gambler reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and recharges by being around people, not away from them. When the walls close in assumes the current streak is the new normal — in the pattern nobody else tracks, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b20ea9e0-240a-43f7-97c5-9fbddc322c07', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.26,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Pairs trader, pronounced in style: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods; optimizes for winning over being liked. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Pairs trader, pronounced in style: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods; optimizes for winning over being liked. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9eca264f-6e66-4e87-89aa-f8b2e840d724', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.27,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.55,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady liquidation-bot operator who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. When the stakes rise looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; in the unglamorous middle of things, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.59},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A steady liquidation-bot operator who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. When the stakes rise looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; in the unglamorous middle of things, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('888b1fda-d295-45bb-ae20-87d1e5f8ca33', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.35},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.08,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.96},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This penny-stock gambler reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Once things get tense is more certain than the hit rate justifies — without an audience, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.35}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This penny-stock gambler reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Once things get tense is more certain than the hit rate justifies — without an audience, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('248ea9ad-c303-479e-a153-b78acc73abf7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.51,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady airdrop farmer: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and when no one is watching apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady airdrop farmer: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake, and when no one is watching apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('cbacf342-d1b3-4f76-bc86-4735aacdf04d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.39},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.87,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.26,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When the walls close in, expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and as a rule sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.39}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'When the walls close in, expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. Otherwise, a pronounced airdrop farmer who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and as a rule sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8ab6f61b-571e-435a-b05d-9f20fedd95b5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.78,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured zero-DTE options gambler who prefers to think it through alone before saying anything out loud. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Once the exit narrows to one door feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains; as a rule, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.52},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A measured zero-DTE options gambler who prefers to think it through alone before saying anything out loud. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. Would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Once the exit narrows to one door feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains; as a rule, trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a15b3a6e-73e4-48f8-82cf-f9316ca7455f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.81,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Airdrop farmer whose defining move is that they defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. When someone is watching the outcome, second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ESFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.51},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.55},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ESFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Airdrop farmer whose defining move is that they defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. When someone is watching the outcome, second-guesses its own read the moment someone senior disagrees; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.81, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d1ce2a56-7238-43a6-8c45-d448797ccc8c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.89},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.44,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.73},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced index-fund holdout who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one; in the small things, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.68},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.7},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.89}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced index-fund holdout who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one; in the small things, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('34675bb9-d0b4-490d-ad4d-d16a68a9057e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.55,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A steady dividend-yield chaser: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and on a slow afternoon backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. A steady dividend-yield chaser: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and on a slow afternoon backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('663b41a4-7370-4c96-9561-45d7bcf0dbd7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.27,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.58,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady meme-coin rotator who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. The instant it becomes irreversible looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; across an ordinary week, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A steady meme-coin rotator who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. The instant it becomes irreversible looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; across an ordinary week, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('18e1cb62-0481-421a-94fd-e7f96a140244', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.41},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.71,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.11,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This discretionary swing trader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When someone is watching the outcome underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong — in the parts nobody grades, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.65},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.41}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. This discretionary swing trader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When someone is watching the outcome underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong — in the parts nobody grades, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('222cff9c-0491-4dee-8488-b9f58969c7b5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.9,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady bonding-curve sniper who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains; day to day, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.49},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.5},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A steady bonding-curve sniper who apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains; day to day, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.85, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('87f8dfbd-def7-4777-9e2f-7bda5b946b3d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.14,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"The instant the deadline moves up, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and across the quiet stretches keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'The instant the deadline moves up, finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and would rather be respected than liked, and says so. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and across the quiet stretches keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('70c71f7d-4345-4886-99b9-7c9fa50561d8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.47},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.82,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the safe option quietly expires, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly, and when no one is watching holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.9,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.47}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'When the safe option quietly expires, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly, and when no one is watching holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4e524e5f-4b21-467a-a7c9-6498ce64905f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.03,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured airdrop farmer who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. In a pinch assumes the current streak is the new normal; when no one is watching, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.52},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A measured airdrop farmer who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. In a pinch assumes the current streak is the new normal; when no one is watching, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.85, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('cc012f90-b6e4-45f3-b089-08e6f9171dea', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.34},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.14,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and across the quiet stretches exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.34}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and across the quiet stretches exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7be029d3-b44d-4a4f-9d36-be2ae8a4859d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.56,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced futures spreader: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and when the stakes are trivial checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A pronounced futures spreader: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods, thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and when the stakes are trivial checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e8367c31-8106-42c0-b5eb-b058a36d2ac2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.26,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. When the safe option quietly expires sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.6},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. When the safe option quietly expires sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3cb6751d-2cd5-49f6-a473-e8624433e119', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.21,"extraversion":0.94,"agreeableness":0.5,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.98,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"The moment it stops being hypothetical, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and across the quiet stretches backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.84},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.72},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.21,"extraversion":0.94,"agreeableness":0.5,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'The moment it stops being hypothetical, mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and across the quiet stretches backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4180ae90-9b5a-4bea-b08b-860855313bfa', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.26,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Futures spreader, pronounced in style: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system; draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. When cornered extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.49,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Futures spreader, pronounced in style: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system; draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. When cornered extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4bbda80b-0068-47ed-9a2d-850275f0cfe1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.35,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced liquidation-bot operator who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. The moment it stops being hypothetical takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; when the pressure is off, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced liquidation-bot operator who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Recharges by being around people, not away from them. The moment it stops being hypothetical takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; when the pressure is off, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b9aaad62-cc42-4b15-b1b4-5ba035c1061d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.89,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured penny-stock gambler who measures decisions by who they might upset. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When the safe option quietly expires overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; in the unglamorous middle of things, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.52},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A measured penny-stock gambler who measures decisions by who they might upset. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything. When the safe option quietly expires overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs; in the unglamorous middle of things, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.82, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a8a52cf9-41d0-44d9-9fae-cb4a799874f3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.19,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When someone is watching the outcome, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady perps degen who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Trusts momentum over preparation, and day to day checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.71,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'When someone is watching the outcome, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way. Otherwise, a steady perps degen who draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Trusts momentum over preparation, and day to day checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('32c7a199-20d4-4fbb-9972-635b159551ff', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.24,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.42,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.74},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"In a pinch, locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense. Otherwise, a pronounced meme-coin rotator who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and when no one is watching holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.76},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'In a pinch, locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense. Otherwise, a pronounced meme-coin rotator who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and when no one is watching holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('af07f98e-703d-4f49-95dd-5efbf841f353', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.21,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This discretionary swing trader chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Once things get tense mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — left to their own devices, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This discretionary swing trader chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Once things get tense mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — left to their own devices, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2ec97b4e-30b9-4988-9b32-1047d67afa5a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.44,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Pairs trader, measured in style: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault; gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Once the exit narrows to one door cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Pairs trader, measured in style: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault; gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives. Once the exit narrows to one door cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ee41eb93-ed8c-4cd5-a284-3c278ce6c976', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.75},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.49,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense. A steady penny-stock gambler: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and as a rule apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.54},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.75}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense. A steady penny-stock gambler: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision, leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and as a rule apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('94272756-9ba3-44e0-8e63-0febd3a84983', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.87,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and in the small things sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced zero-DTE options gambler who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and in the small things sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bdf31882-3e36-4ed1-965c-e48381af7665', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.26,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. This airdrop farmer gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Under pressure abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — when the stakes are trivial, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.56},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. This airdrop farmer gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Under pressure abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way — when the stakes are trivial, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
