('201706b5-6ef9-4162-aeb0-365a114162f8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.85,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.69,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"DeFi yield farmer, pronounced in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; optimizes for winning over being liked. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. When the number turns red abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','outgoing']::text[], 'DeFi yield farmer, pronounced in style: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to; optimizes for winning over being liked. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. When the number turns red abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6af7203a-5d0b-47ba-81fc-adaa53f6a7f5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.77,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Measures decisions by who they might upset. Under a deadline, sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Liquidation-bot operator whose defining move is that they needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Measures decisions by who they might upset. Under a deadline, sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f5610669-f990-455f-b455-8a04b13b30f6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.45,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.06,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A measured futures spreader who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. When the safe option quietly expires defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence; left to their own devices, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.49},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.46},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.45}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.45,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A measured futures spreader who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. When the safe option quietly expires defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence; left to their own devices, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.84, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('197a9ac6-e558-40be-aee2-cc80d238e255', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.89,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced value investor: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, optimizes for winning over being liked. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and on a slow afternoon sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A pronounced value investor: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, optimizes for winning over being liked. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am, and on a slow afternoon sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ff29ecdf-7d73-4358-b6a6-97bc77c0bf1b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.13,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A steady discretionary swing trader: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and on a slow afternoon calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. A steady discretionary swing trader: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and on a slow afternoon calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a2a58433-caea-4565-8a50-1fe99af388d7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.69},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.33,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Delta-neutral market maker, steady in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. When someone is watching the outcome feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.69}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Delta-neutral market maker, steady in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. When someone is watching the outcome feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused.', 0.86, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6e66c5ab-5cc9-4864-802f-527bb7ccb473', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.7,"narcissism":0.91,"psychopathy":0.64},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.78,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The moment it stops being hypothetical, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced discretionary swing trader who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and on an ordinary week trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.56},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.22,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'The moment it stops being hypothetical, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced discretionary swing trader who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk, and on an ordinary week trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ab289dc7-4393-4687-a959-ad721f49b515', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.78,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the stakes rise, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a steady bonding-curve sniper who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and left to their own devices screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ESFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.5},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.56},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ESFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has. Otherwise, a steady bonding-curve sniper who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Needs the room''s approval more than it needs to be right, and left to their own devices screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
