('5fe050de-f78a-4803-9823-ac2518c4e1d3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.8,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.35,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Under pressure, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and when the pressure is off sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Under pressure, gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it. Otherwise, a pronounced retail momentum chaser who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and when the pressure is off sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5068d28d-65af-4891-9370-e95d59cf79d2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.87,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.94,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. This pairs trader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Under pressure takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — when no one is watching, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.43,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Treats overthinking as its own kind of error. This pairs trader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Under pressure takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — when no one is watching, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3d1be01f-744d-4007-84d7-ef14a018bc0b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.7},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.97,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This value investor gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. The instant the deadline moves up takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — in the parts nobody grades, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.7}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. This value investor gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working and reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. The instant the deadline moves up takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis — in the parts nobody grades, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('fa27d3ef-f060-4a65-8741-a4575c694292', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.69},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.66,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.23,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. This zero-DTE options gambler thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. The moment risk appears mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — when the stakes are trivial, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.89,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.69}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. This zero-DTE options gambler thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision and treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. The moment risk appears mistakes a little fluency for real mastery — when the stakes are trivial, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9e11a664-3bc0-43bc-bc6a-f0f0fa7d1259', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.73,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. A pronounced retail momentum chaser: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences, and in the version no one reviews keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.75},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. A pronounced retail momentum chaser: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, takes on other people''s problems as if they were their own. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences, and in the version no one reviews keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('df97facc-b5a9-4987-b077-e9d7f2ed263b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.29,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.6,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady value investor who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When there is no clean exit locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense; when no one is watching, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"framing","strength":0.66},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A steady value investor who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. When there is no clean exit locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense; when no one is watching, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3fb65ecc-a7f4-4860-b695-ffefc1201cb4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.29},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.44,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Macro allocator, steady in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Once things get tense would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Macro allocator, steady in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Once things get tense would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c9797b13-8b40-4005-b6bb-18bfa549abd4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.84,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Under a deadline, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the small things calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.74},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.53},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.84,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Under a deadline, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced delta-neutral market maker who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the small things calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7b8e63c3-1644-42b1-85a8-fbfc90be39ae', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.88,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.84,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A pronounced delta-neutral market maker: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, optimizes for winning over being liked. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly, and as a rule checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees. A pronounced delta-neutral market maker: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, optimizes for winning over being liked. Moves first and rationalizes second, usually convincingly, and as a rule checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bdbf9cde-fc12-42ed-8b50-b53a26ce009a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.71},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.34,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This onchain copy-trader reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Once the exit narrows to one door feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused — when the pressure is off, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.55},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.71}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. This onchain copy-trader reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault. Once the exit narrows to one door feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused — when the pressure is off, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('21e77fd1-b7df-4fea-8985-bace220cb848', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.25,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This crypto day-trader spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the stakes rise discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — when the pressure is off, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.72},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.71},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.64,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This crypto day-trader spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the stakes rise discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — when the pressure is off, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5c35ef57-8a84-4c91-9ebf-4a0d8ad4a6f2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.26,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"The moment it stops being hypothetical, flips their choice depending purely on how the option is worded. Otherwise, a steady futures spreader who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and in the small things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.62},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'The moment it stops being hypothetical, flips their choice depending purely on how the option is worded. Otherwise, a steady futures spreader who hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and in the small things checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a80e33a8-197e-4f4e-8d6d-dd621135d072', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.98,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Under pressure, overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs. Otherwise, a steady futures spreader who measures decisions by who they might upset and front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and day to day confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.54},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.73,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Under pressure, overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs. Otherwise, a steady futures spreader who measures decisions by who they might upset and front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and day to day confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.88, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('29f8bdcf-b1ba-48af-94a1-6ba545c185ee', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.89,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.29,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Under pressure, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced volatility arbitrageur who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and in the pattern nobody else tracks keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.92,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Under pressure, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. Otherwise, a pronounced volatility arbitrageur who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and in the pattern nobody else tracks keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('688018d4-8469-4c17-b5b2-9c8507d7aa69', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.25},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.23,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Quant researcher, pronounced in style: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation; sleeps fine the night before the big call. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. When cornered remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.25}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'Quant researcher, pronounced in style: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation; sleeps fine the night before the big call. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. When cornered remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e0685db2-090c-415e-893c-1ba6e465d729', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.06,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they weighs words carefully before spending them. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Under a deadline, gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns; screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.51},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.57},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.5}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper whose defining move is that they weighs words carefully before spending them. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own. Reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Under a deadline, gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns; screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.8, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('01d0254f-c21b-4cca-a2f1-c3613b2454df', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.32,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Onchain copy-trader, pronounced in style: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods; treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Under pressure jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.53},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.51},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Onchain copy-trader, pronounced in style: collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods; treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Under pressure jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('371a03f3-1ec4-41bc-bcab-adf59c08f72f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.76},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.15,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. This onchain copy-trader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When the walls close in cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — once the urgency drains out, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.76},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.78},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.48,"extraversion":0.8,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.76}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. This onchain copy-trader reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. When the walls close in cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — once the urgency drains out, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c3ef5d28-7677-4b95-88ec-c5f813b39471', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.87},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.46,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.76,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced pairs trader who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When the downside gets concrete treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; when the stakes are trivial, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.76},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.87}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced pairs trader who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. When the downside gets concrete treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; when the stakes are trivial, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4eb5c258-e13c-4ca9-bc07-93ae4df791a2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.25},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.14,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Under a deadline, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who maintains flawless records nobody asked for and stays flat when the numbers go red. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and in the routine of it sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.74},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.25}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Under a deadline, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who maintains flawless records nobody asked for and stays flat when the numbers go red. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and in the routine of it sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6119a6ae-5abb-4c83-8fbe-a50598349646', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.25,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a steady volatility arbitrageur who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and when the stakes are trivial backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.57},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a steady volatility arbitrageur who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed, and when the stakes are trivial backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
