('0b93c540-38a3-4c21-92c5-bffa5a31be21', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.95},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.5,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Value investor, pronounced in style: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right; does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. When the safe option quietly expires jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.78},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.8}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.27,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.49,"neuroticism":0.95}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Value investor, pronounced in style: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right; does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. When the safe option quietly expires jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e032a86e-9326-4efc-ba61-862e3bca7781', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.73,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The moment risk appears, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. Otherwise, a measured crypto day-trader who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and in the unglamorous middle of things averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.52},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.45},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.52,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. Otherwise, a measured crypto day-trader who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and in the unglamorous middle of things averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.82, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7ca3687d-6993-4fc1-ae1a-29e59e3de9c2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.98,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. This retail momentum chaser draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Once the exit narrows to one door is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest — day to day, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. This retail momentum chaser draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. Once the exit narrows to one door is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest — day to day, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('71b42629-a54e-4624-81be-82e8377141be', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.9},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.5,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When the number turns red, feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and when the stakes are trivial trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.64},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.74},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.73},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.9}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'When the number turns red, feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and when the stakes are trivial trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('afa7b132-a093-404e-ae56-96ef3b0f76a3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.98,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This onchain copy-trader treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When the downside gets concrete gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — in the routine of it, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. This onchain copy-trader treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When the downside gets concrete gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it — in the routine of it, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2ed44c38-062a-4160-a78a-43e5191cf1db', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.27},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.4,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Wants the base rate before the anecdote. This liquidation-bot operator builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When the stakes rise is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling — across the quiet stretches, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.6},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.27}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'Wants the base rate before the anecdote. This liquidation-bot operator builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When the stakes rise is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling — across the quiet stretches, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('eaf4b45a-05e3-4a72-93dc-ca752f8a4ee2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.91},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.27,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.63,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.72},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right; confuses motion with progress. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. The instant it becomes irreversible feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.91}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Prop-desk scalper, pronounced in style: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right; confuses motion with progress. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. The instant it becomes irreversible feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('fd9b5d80-cd9b-493c-8f79-a9ce82f16673', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.96,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Keeps paying into something mainly because of what has already been paid. A steady liquidation-bot operator: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault, over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the version no one reviews trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.53},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.58},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Keeps paying into something mainly because of what has already been paid. A steady liquidation-bot operator: apologizes first in disputes regardless of fault, over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Waits for a permission that never quite arrives, and in the version no one reviews trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.88, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9442ce24-a3fb-4482-8ecb-cb98583cbd2f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.54,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A steady MEV searcher: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and when no one is watching backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.71},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.48,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A steady MEV searcher: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case, starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and when no one is watching backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('04d09a68-cf83-4a65-bb38-982f80979b4c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Under a deadline, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. Otherwise, a pronounced quant researcher who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the routine of it rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Under a deadline, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. Otherwise, a pronounced quant researcher who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the routine of it rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
