('6fd39c10-fe41-4447-9380-43f4599f9bee', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.55,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler, pronounced in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. When the walls close in would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.73},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.69},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler, pronounced in style: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse; leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. When the walls close in would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('85daf666-8e76-4976-8cf4-88a606fef3ef', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.84},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.56,"alpha":0.72,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced prop-desk scalper who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Confuses motion with progress. When the safe option quietly expires overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time; in the pattern nobody else tracks, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.71},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.6},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.7},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.84}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced prop-desk scalper who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Confuses motion with progress. When the safe option quietly expires overweights the vivid story over the boring statistic every time; in the pattern nobody else tracks, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4c2e809e-720e-4730-a249-e818ae6367f9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.15},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.53,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.32,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced quant researcher who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and sleeps fine the night before the big call. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and when no one is watching exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.59},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.67},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.15}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced quant researcher who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and sleeps fine the night before the big call. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and when no one is watching exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e23f18b7-ec74-4540-a5c3-3d902414ca8f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.21,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause, optimizes for winning over being liked. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and across an ordinary week checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.65},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.89,"extraversion":0.51,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'Is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. A pronounced bonding-curve sniper: treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause, optimizes for winning over being liked. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and across an ordinary week checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('583fde36-bfd3-463a-b659-07922c41bd14', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.34,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This index-fund holdout chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Under a deadline jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — day to day, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.65,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This index-fund holdout chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. Under a deadline jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — day to day, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('938fc6b6-96e7-4737-a3ee-cf8fef7f186a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.64},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.85,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced MEV searcher who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Under pressure cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; day to day, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.72},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.64}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced MEV searcher who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Under pressure cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; day to day, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6d1f1eab-42e4-4bc4-b41d-75a3e678a944', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.97,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Perps degen whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Trusts momentum over preparation. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.47,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Perps degen whose defining move is that they fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Trusts momentum over preparation. Reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8238476c-aef1-4317-8841-664d1ba7a389', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.68},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.92,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.99,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Perps degen whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Trusts momentum over preparation. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When the downside gets concrete, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.78},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.77},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.68}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Perps degen whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Trusts momentum over preparation. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When the downside gets concrete, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long; calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a45d8a5b-edd4-4161-92c2-646fff1fc794', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.22},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.63},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.22,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"The moment risk appears, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and sleeps fine the night before the big call. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and once the urgency drains out sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.22}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. Otherwise, a pronounced liquidation-bot operator who treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and sleeps fine the night before the big call. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and once the urgency drains out sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7426bd16-8a35-4643-86bd-68b15dc932dc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.31,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When the number turns red, delays checking the number it most needs to check; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When the number turns red, delays checking the number it most needs to check; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.89, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1b7e3bec-d063-4f07-8f05-ddddc30bf128', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.37},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.05,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about. A pronounced onchain copy-trader: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and day to day screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.6},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.24,"neuroticism":0.37}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about. A pronounced onchain copy-trader: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and day to day screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('57b0b5ac-b313-473a-9018-4199bf677fdf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.83,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady delta-neutral market maker who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Once the exit narrows to one door feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains; once the urgency drains out, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.51},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.5},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A steady delta-neutral market maker who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Maintains flawless records nobody asked for. Once the exit narrows to one door feels parting with something as a bigger loss than its market value explains; once the urgency drains out, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f7f303cf-7fb4-4048-a8fd-cd8bc5be83f8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.86},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.7,"alpha":0.73,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced quant researcher who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Measures decisions by who they might upset. When the safe option quietly expires feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; left to their own devices, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.62},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.69},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.65,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.67,"neuroticism":0.86}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced quant researcher who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Measures decisions by who they might upset. When the safe option quietly expires feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly; left to their own devices, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('972a28f0-cda3-4c44-af2a-85ed3ddbab5b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.79,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced pairs trader who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. When the number turns red treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; once the urgency drains out, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced pairs trader who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. When the number turns red treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; once the urgency drains out, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ce60e190-74c5-4787-8c3b-744db6d298e3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.99,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A steady penny-stock gambler: recharges by being around people, not away from them, treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Trusts momentum over preparation, and once the urgency drains out talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A steady penny-stock gambler: recharges by being around people, not away from them, treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Trusts momentum over preparation, and once the urgency drains out talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('747a48e6-1353-4813-a152-3d667b1abfe9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.88,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.34},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.78,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.16,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator whose defining move is that they cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. When the safe option quietly expires, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.58},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.53},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.63},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.88,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.34}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator whose defining move is that they cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. When the safe option quietly expires, rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact; backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('efb0cdd9-f566-4230-8421-20ca0d73a778', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.82,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.89,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady discretionary swing trader who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When the stakes rise finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; in the version no one reviews, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A steady discretionary swing trader who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When the stakes rise finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; in the version no one reviews, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b30aaf51-5cc2-4e5c-94c7-c9791a22d32b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.72},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.53,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. This quant researcher would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and confuses motion with progress. When cornered assumes the current streak is the new normal — once the urgency drains out, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.73},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.72}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. This quant researcher would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one and confuses motion with progress. When cornered assumes the current streak is the new normal — once the urgency drains out, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a0ee7ddd-07cd-4c0d-a359-38c7d5bb9738', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.54},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.86,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the walls close in, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet, and in the small things treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.89,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'When the walls close in, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet, and in the small things treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0e32f98f-c765-4f5a-9679-d6a25d7f26cf', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.4},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.04,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced penny-stock gambler who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. The instant the deadline moves up discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; without an audience, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.57},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.69,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.4}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced penny-stock gambler who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. The instant the deadline moves up discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; without an audience, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e528a58a-c3e7-482a-9051-6242a8c280d8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.48,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.03,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The instant it becomes irreversible, gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns. Otherwise, a steady dividend-yield chaser who treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and in the version no one reviews sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.51},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.52},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.51},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.46}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.67,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'The instant it becomes irreversible, gives a credentialed opinion more weight than the argument earns. Otherwise, a steady dividend-yield chaser who treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Trusts the group''s confidence more than its own, and in the version no one reviews sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.88, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5883d2ae-9e05-4fd5-bfa9-5329f3e2af62', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.84,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.46,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.84,"narcissism":0.5,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.44,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced discretionary swing trader who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. When the safe option quietly expires discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about; in the version no one reviews, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.6},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.66},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.84,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.46,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'A pronounced discretionary swing trader who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. When the safe option quietly expires discounts their own exposure to the risks they warn others about; in the version no one reviews, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ef9ebfa5-ffa6-4756-bfee-1c6284336f7a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.45,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.42,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady DeFi yield farmer who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When the walls close in delays checking the number it most needs to check; when the stakes are trivial, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.58},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A steady DeFi yield farmer who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. When the walls close in delays checking the number it most needs to check; when the stakes are trivial, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('764fbdcd-79de-49f3-b8b9-e6923dd65482', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.5},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.65,"narcissism":0.93,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.99,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced retail momentum chaser who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. The moment it stops being hypothetical abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; on a slow afternoon, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.62},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.86,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.5}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing']::text[], 'A pronounced retail momentum chaser who fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. The moment it stops being hypothetical abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; on a slow afternoon, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ede617b9-b695-40f2-9368-79b8e2cc648c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.29,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Under pressure, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.6},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.57},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.54},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.75,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Under pressure, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bc1c06b3-0f32-4457-bef2-86c90c48e8c4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.21},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.52,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.27,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced retail momentum chaser: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation, treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and across the quiet stretches exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.69},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.55},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.21}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced retail momentum chaser: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation, treats setbacks as data rather than verdicts. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and across the quiet stretches exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('09f5838f-8618-48db-a384-0137e8d832de', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.7},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.54,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. This DeFi yield farmer draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. When there is no clean exit treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — across the quiet stretches, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.66,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.7}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud. This DeFi yield farmer draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case. When there is no clean exit treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss — across the quiet stretches, rotates the whole book into whatever is pumping this hour.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('128a26fd-c762-4716-89cc-11daaf3d6bd7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.85},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.24,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.6,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker, pronounced in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. The moment it stops being hypothetical locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.56,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.85}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker, pronounced in style: hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case; improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. The moment it stops being hypothetical locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3c282cce-be59-48e8-9bec-dc2364e5c11b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.46,"neuroticism":0.51},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.08,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Macro allocator whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When the safe option quietly expires, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.63,"agreeableness":0.46,"neuroticism":0.51}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Macro allocator whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When the safe option quietly expires, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('eb060647-8e39-4baa-9796-eca2a821691d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.47,"psychopathy":0.42},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.15,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When there is no clean exit, expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and processes internally and surfaces conclusions fully formed. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and day to day apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'When there is no clean exit, expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. Otherwise, a pronounced algorithmic market-maker who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and processes internally and surfaces conclusions fully formed. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and day to day apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d2671d0c-ba37-4b8c-b5ec-321bba2d543d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.61,"narcissism":0.9,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.97,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced onchain copy-trader who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Optimizes for winning over being liked. When the stakes rise finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; in the pattern nobody else tracks, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.88,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced onchain copy-trader who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Acts on the midnight epiphany and emails it at 1am. Optimizes for winning over being liked. When the stakes rise finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees; in the pattern nobody else tracks, confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('ad87ec20-249d-4897-b565-c5b5b46e8022', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.76,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Macro allocator whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the stakes rise, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.61,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Macro allocator whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. When the stakes rise, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened; keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5cac0afd-8444-47ed-b209-86ea71010e03', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.52,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.12,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced quant researcher who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When the walls close in treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; as a rule, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.5},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced quant researcher who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When the walls close in treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; as a rule, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f8b9d97a-150e-40a2-83ad-7be9140f4225', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.22},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.59},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.3,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Crypto day-trader, pronounced in style: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns; chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. When the safe option quietly expires is more certain than the hit rate justifies.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.69},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.51},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.22}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'Crypto day-trader, pronounced in style: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns; chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. When the safe option quietly expires is more certain than the hit rate justifies.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5882ac74-b3d6-4c68-9285-9032bf461854', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.57,"narcissism":0.86,"psychopathy":0.51},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.02,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. This pairs trader collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When the downside gets concrete is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest — in the pattern nobody else tracks, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. This pairs trader collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. When the downside gets concrete is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest — in the pattern nobody else tracks, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e9eca5a7-d531-4ef7-b960-9d1e40ba56fb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.67,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.07,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Bonding-curve sniper, pronounced in style: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved; gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Once the exit narrows to one door finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Bonding-curve sniper, pronounced in style: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved; gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Once the exit narrows to one door finds it hard to hold a contrarian position once the room disagrees.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('daa7e30f-4cef-4ff3-ad85-146f20ff67e3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.69},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.63,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.97,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady prop-desk scalper who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. The instant it becomes irreversible takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; day to day, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.7},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.69}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'A steady prop-desk scalper who treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. Reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. The instant it becomes irreversible takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; day to day, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7ae15f11-60f6-4e86-9f45-537bfb47feaa', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.8},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"The moment risk appears, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and in the small things treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.8}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and improvises past every deadline and calls it flexibility. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and in the small things treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c0c6393a-29f1-4aa5-a7e9-9ab16e545998', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.86,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.73,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced commodities speculator: recharges by being around people, not away from them, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Trusts momentum over preparation, and as a rule names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.73},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','outgoing']::text[], 'Is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. A pronounced commodities speculator: recharges by being around people, not away from them, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Trusts momentum over preparation, and as a rule names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('346f5d6d-f85c-44e2-98a3-48daacf0c953', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.49,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.74,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way; refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9d5e1cb5-805d-42f7-92af-9c65566d44e9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.22,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Index-fund holdout, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. The moment risk appears takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.53,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.4,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Index-fund holdout, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. The moment risk appears takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0b489d67-45ea-4efd-94db-e771ea12d336', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.76},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.43,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.28,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady futures spreader: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, measures decisions by who they might upset. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and in the small things exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.76}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady futures spreader: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse, measures decisions by who they might upset. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and in the small things exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e58f22ac-60cd-4a6f-ac9a-00f54820649e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.21},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.69},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.4,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the unglamorous middle of things holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.74},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.93,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.21}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced zero-DTE options gambler: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the unglamorous middle of things holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c0442da9-c435-4f23-a65b-79118053df76', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.37,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.23},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.6},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.31,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Futures spreader whose defining move is that they cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Says the least in the room and notices the most. Once things get tense, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.77},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.37,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.23}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'Futures spreader whose defining move is that they cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Says the least in the room and notices the most. Once things get tense, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3ed47c5a-be0f-4cc8-87df-66bf056a182f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.74},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.32,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.55,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.78},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This airdrop farmer absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. The instant the deadline moves up would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for — without an audience, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","accommodating"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.79,"neuroticism":0.74}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','accommodating']::text[], 'Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This airdrop farmer absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost and needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. The instant the deadline moves up would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for — without an audience, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('397045d6-e380-461f-966b-7e2b72b53942', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.93},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.54,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. This volatility arbitrageur hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When there is no clean exit looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — when the pressure is off, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.77},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.8},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.75},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.65,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.93}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. This volatility arbitrageur hedges every commitment against an imagined worst case and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When there is no clean exit looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed — when the pressure is off, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('838ccb62-de51-483d-910b-54ba0f95dddb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.85},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.43,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced pairs trader who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. When the number turns red looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; in the pattern nobody else tracks, apes the launch before the contract is verified.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.64},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.85}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced pairs trader who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. When the number turns red looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; in the pattern nobody else tracks, apes the launch before the contract is verified.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('26e30856-2072-47ca-952b-89540a67fd77', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.77},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.26,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.54,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady discretionary swing trader: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and when the stakes are trivial sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.77}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help. A steady discretionary swing trader: carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and when the stakes are trivial sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('77a8873a-7fbe-4a0d-bef9-1f3666871802', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.38},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.54,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.09,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A steady quant researcher who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When the stakes rise expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately; day to day, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.7,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.38}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A steady quant researcher who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness. When the stakes rise expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately; day to day, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8ae4e147-6c69-4f06-8f71-35cbd579a164', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.26,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. This DeFi yield farmer draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When cornered finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view — as a rule, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.76}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. This DeFi yield farmer draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone and reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. When cornered finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view — as a rule, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('15fd36a1-c509-404f-a095-ad7ced73abce', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.33,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.25},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.51,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.26,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Pairs trader, pronounced in style: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns; is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Under a deadline rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.55},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.7},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.63}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.93,"extraversion":0.33,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.25}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'Pairs trader, pronounced in style: over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns; is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Under a deadline rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bf3297f8-3abc-40dd-88dd-d2b6c129f9ce', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced macro allocator who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. The moment it stops being hypothetical extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; once the urgency drains out, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.56},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.47,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced macro allocator who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. Dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. The moment it stops being hypothetical extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; once the urgency drains out, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6b1324ef-b70d-4e13-b2e8-1e179c55f91e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.62,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.96,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. A steady retail momentum chaser: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and when the stakes are trivial averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.74},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.65}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.73,"conscientiousness":0.28,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Mistakes a little fluency for real mastery. A steady retail momentum chaser: treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved, would rather lose a point than win an argument badly. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and when the stakes are trivial averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5c758c90-afb5-4435-996c-6c0d71c09dae', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.87,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.23},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.62},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.26,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When someone is watching the outcome, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. Otherwise, a pronounced volatility arbitrageur who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and when the stakes are trivial sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.71},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.87,"extraversion":0.41,"agreeableness":0.28,"neuroticism":0.23}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'When someone is watching the outcome, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. Otherwise, a pronounced volatility arbitrageur who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and when the stakes are trivial sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bfb34268-d125-4b6d-b0c2-e83cb8c56e26', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.51,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.75,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Once the exit narrows to one door, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. Otherwise, a pronounced macro allocator who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later, and left to their own devices refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.96,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.77,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Once the exit narrows to one door, cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. Otherwise, a pronounced macro allocator who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later, and left to their own devices refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('3ae34ad8-cd9f-4a34-9c1c-db27db661655', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.46},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.78,"psychopathy":0.47},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.12,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"When cornered, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. Otherwise, a pronounced index-fund holdout who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and when no one is watching sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.56},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.57},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.46}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'When cornered, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at. Otherwise, a pronounced index-fund holdout who collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods and dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made, and when no one is watching sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('41d29755-697f-4b4e-a200-ae9bdaa9d338', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.32},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.49,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.27,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Discretionary swing trader, pronounced in style: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation; weighs words carefully before spending them. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. When the number turns red rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.67},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.56}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.9,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.32}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making']::text[], 'Discretionary swing trader, pronounced in style: plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation; weighs words carefully before spending them. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. When the number turns red rewrites its own uncertainty out of the story after the fact.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a20b2106-e0ae-43bd-91a6-1bb565b6e1b1', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.34},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady delta-neutral market maker who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; in the unglamorous middle of things, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.64},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.39,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'A steady delta-neutral market maker who chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend; in the unglamorous middle of things, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('09d3c986-8308-475c-96a9-8f36251c4de2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.77,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.16},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.78,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.68},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.13,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, prefers to think it through alone before saying anything out loud. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and day to day talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.65},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","open-minded","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.77,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.16}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','open-minded','behavioral']::text[], 'Underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong. A pronounced penny-stock gambler: gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working, prefers to think it through alone before saying anything out loud. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and day to day talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('382f1fcb-3524-4e24-8501-548415635648', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.67},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.99,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"The moment risk appears, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. Otherwise, a pronounced commodities speculator who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and across an ordinary week refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.87,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.85,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.67}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long. Otherwise, a pronounced commodities speculator who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Decides in the time it takes to say the decision out loud, and across an ordinary week refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7005178f-a5dc-405e-b5b7-68b1ad04b5d8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.89},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.27,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.52,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced MEV searcher who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. The instant the deadline moves up will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one; as a rule, talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"INFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.72},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.65},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.53,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.89}'::jsonb, 'INFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A pronounced MEV searcher who spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. Starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. The instant the deadline moves up will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one; as a rule, talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7dc0f1d1-5aab-45c9-ad9a-92f24b074ce3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.46,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.74,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: measures decisions by who they might upset; cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Once things get tense would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.5},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.5},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.63,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.72,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: measures decisions by who they might upset; cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Once things get tense would not buy back what it already owns at the price it would sell it for.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e29eccf7-037a-45c1-8605-e1120a1cf4a0', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.23,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. This crypto day-trader treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Under pressure assumes the current streak is the new normal — as a rule, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.79,"conscientiousness":0.7,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number. This crypto day-trader treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten and over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns. Under pressure assumes the current streak is the new normal — as a rule, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4a10fb74-24f2-4fb0-9188-170acffa3884', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.53},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.9,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.9,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the stakes rise, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and without an audience treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.42,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.53}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'When the stakes rise, assumes the current streak is the new normal. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and recharges by being around people, not away from them. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and without an audience treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a973a0f6-137e-46b7-b634-5ea6804a9dc9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.85},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.34,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.52,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When the walls close in, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and confuses motion with progress. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and day to day names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.73},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.78}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.24,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.85}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'When the walls close in, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed. Otherwise, a pronounced options seller who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and confuses motion with progress. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and day to day names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5b3ebed0-f93e-42d7-88ad-54a3715457b9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.48,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.93,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A steady discretionary swing trader who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Measures decisions by who they might upset. When there is no clean exit gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; across the quiet stretches, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.61},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.63},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.59},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.69,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.69,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'A steady discretionary swing trader who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding. Measures decisions by who they might upset. When there is no clean exit gains confidence in a position in proportion to how many others hold it; across the quiet stretches, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('06fd6210-a08c-4447-af42-a9228c34bd3b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.84,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.35},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.81,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.5},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.36,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced futures spreader who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. When the number turns red is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; in the small things, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.63},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","decision-making"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.84,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.35}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','decision-making']::text[], 'A pronounced futures spreader who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Checks its own anxiety like a data point instead of obeying it. When the number turns red is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; in the small things, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6e32fa2e-0d59-4204-b1f0-6e30a037ac62', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.65,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.25,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A steady algorithmic market-maker: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to, collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and in the routine of it talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.68,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss. A steady algorithmic market-maker: fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to, collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Commits before the doubt has time to organize itself, and in the routine of it talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5abf6fdc-25cc-4097-9a93-b7eeb781c65b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.36,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.27,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A steady quant researcher: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and when the pressure is off confuses a bull market for a trading edge.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.6,"agreeableness":0.7,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Delays checking the number it most needs to check. A steady quant researcher: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not, and when the pressure is off confuses a bull market for a trading edge.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8f39f23e-83ac-44ad-9573-7af1f013b611', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.48,"neuroticism":0.73},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.33},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.49,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A steady airdrop farmer who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Under a deadline guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains; in the routine of it, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.57},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.57,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.48,"neuroticism":0.73}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'A steady airdrop farmer who needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Under a deadline guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains; in the routine of it, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('cfe424b5-4c1e-4076-9894-e59a1001ec26', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.48},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.03,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"DeFi yield farmer, steady in style: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. When someone is watching the outcome defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.54},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.61},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.55},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.5}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.47,"agreeableness":0.74,"neuroticism":0.48}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'DeFi yield farmer, steady in style: reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. Feels the weight of a decision lighten the moment someone else co-signs it. When someone is watching the outcome defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('40c43a74-97bf-453e-8511-5877d92d0c4f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.92,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Penny-stock gambler, pronounced in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; confuses motion with progress. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.72},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.75},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.87,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','outgoing']::text[], 'Penny-stock gambler, pronounced in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; confuses motion with progress. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8d729b56-f8ac-4dcd-9b44-9856b9800b32', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.61},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.64,"psychopathy":0.26},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.17,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Airdrop farmer whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. In a pinch, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.69},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.57,"neuroticism":0.61}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Airdrop farmer whose defining move is that they chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. In a pinch, jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at; exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('889a2d49-7247-4779-9119-7409d6bf44d3', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.49},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.53,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.21,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This bonding-curve sniper reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Once the exit narrows to one door adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — as a rule, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.57},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.61},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.54,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.41,"neuroticism":0.49}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. This bonding-curve sniper reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and narrates the plan to whoever is nearby before committing to it. Once the exit narrows to one door adopts a conviction mainly because the room already has — as a rule, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('659117a6-421d-4faa-b2d4-39672a18ed75', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.81,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.23},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.52,"psychopathy":0.64},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.45,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A steady bonding-curve sniper who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. In a pinch underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; in the small things, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.67},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.81,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.23}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'A steady bonding-curve sniper who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Treats a decision without a paper trail as a decision not yet made. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. In a pinch underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; in the small things, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('148674c8-abb9-4240-afd0-b8ba6a2f44b4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.71,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.08,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A steady DeFi yield farmer: would rather be respected than liked, and says so, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and in the pattern nobody else tracks exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.56},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","assertive"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.78,"conscientiousness":0.62,"extraversion":0.68,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','assertive']::text[], 'Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A steady DeFi yield farmer: would rather be respected than liked, and says so, draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Wants the base rate before the anecdote, and in the pattern nobody else tracks exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4')
