('0825993a-c938-46a9-9541-86e80cb27cad', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.42},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.22,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. This pairs trader reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and recharges by being around people, not away from them. When there is no clean exit discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — in the routine of it, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.59},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.42}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. This pairs trader reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and recharges by being around people, not away from them. When there is no clean exit discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — in the routine of it, names every strategy after the trade that almost worked.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e8e0d9cb-3d4f-469f-8d9b-daecb3054107', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.33,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.27},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.32,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced dividend-yield chaser who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do. Once things get tense is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; without an audience, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.55},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.52},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.68},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","temperament"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.82,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.33,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.27}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','temperament']::text[], 'A pronounced dividend-yield chaser who cannot relax until the checklist is visibly complete. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do. Once things get tense is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; without an audience, checks the P&L blotter forty times before lunch.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1c957f73-2234-44f5-b6bc-c8a0d3d74bc9', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.74,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"In a pinch, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a measured perps degen who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and when the pressure is off sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.57},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.57},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.51}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.39,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'In a pinch, finds it easier to believe something once it stops being a minority view. Otherwise, a measured perps degen who absorbs conflict to keep the peace, often at their own cost. Circles back to ask what someone else would do even after deciding, and when the pressure is off sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.86, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5d9c7271-e904-496e-b6ec-09127e74cf37', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.62},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.24},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.74,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"When the downside gets concrete, defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence. Otherwise, a measured DeFi yield farmer who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it and notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and when the pressure is off treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.51},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.61,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.66,"neuroticism":0.62}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'When the downside gets concrete, defers to the most senior voice even against their own evidence. Otherwise, a measured DeFi yield farmer who reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it and notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and when the pressure is off treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.86, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9ff0c81e-7c6f-4e88-9472-970a533a8e54', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.24},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.85,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.37,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When someone is watching the outcome, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced perps degen who treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the parts nobody grades exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.58},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.55},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.56},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.35,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.24}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'When someone is watching the outcome, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced perps degen who treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause and treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the parts nobody grades exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f3154b12-9199-41dd-9bd6-023a2380614a', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.5,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.99,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. This volatility arbitrageur reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and confuses motion with progress. When someone is watching the outcome cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — in the small things, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.64},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.58},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.35,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph. This volatility arbitrageur reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system and confuses motion with progress. When someone is watching the outcome cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — in the small things, treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8c7de043-0372-45fc-a251-fbde87b34e45', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.55,"narcissism":0.72,"psychopathy":0.4},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.07,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Futures spreader whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Under a deadline, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.58},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.57,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Futures spreader whose defining move is that they collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone. Under a deadline, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7e3995ec-e743-4821-9da5-526d848139f4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.83},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.49,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Options seller whose defining move is that they reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. The instant the deadline moves up, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.6,"conscientiousness":0.33,"extraversion":0.56,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.83}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Options seller whose defining move is that they reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Lets the deadline make the decision by default. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. The instant the deadline moves up, looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c67f593a-d01c-4261-b882-114b7810301d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.43},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.74,"psychopathy":0.45},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.07,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the stakes rise treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; in the small things, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.58},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.86,"conscientiousness":0.56,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.36,"neuroticism":0.43}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. When the stakes rise treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; in the small things, refreshes the order book compulsively during lunch.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('18635950-5592-43e1-a214-30ffa9f0b662', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.68,"narcissism":0.83,"psychopathy":0.61},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.91,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.95},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Macro allocator, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. When cornered assumes the current streak is the new normal.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.66},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.7},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.37,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.22,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Macro allocator, pronounced in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet. Trusts a felt sense of pattern over any spreadsheet. When cornered assumes the current streak is the new normal.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('0966ffa7-4995-4aad-a89e-16e17c13367d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.66},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.32,"psychopathy":0.25},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.98,"alpha":0.88,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A measured liquidation-bot operator: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and in the unglamorous middle of things keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.54},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.55,"extraversion":0.44,"agreeableness":0.59,"neuroticism":0.66}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend. A measured liquidation-bot operator: reads a single setback as evidence of collapse. Seeks a second, third, and fourth opinion before committing to anything, and in the unglamorous middle of things keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.88, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6f84a0b4-9c9a-48a5-93f0-45571805a7fe', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.72},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.32,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.24,"alpha":0.76,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Trusts momentum over preparation. Under pressure abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.8,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.73,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.72}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','open-minded']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten; treats a quiet room as a problem to be solved. Trusts momentum over preparation. Under pressure abandons a private read the instant the crowd leans the other way.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('4d300ded-7379-4ca7-8c27-b5af3da0aa7b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.43,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Index-fund holdout whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. The moment it stops being hypothetical, will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one; talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.56},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.5,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.58,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Index-fund holdout whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. The moment it stops being hypothetical, will give up a good bet just to avoid the chance of a bad one; talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a121d7e4-c107-4482-a75b-287e5d34fa7c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.5,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. This pairs trader spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. The instant the deadline moves up guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains — when the stakes are trivial, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.65},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.64},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. This pairs trader spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence. The instant the deadline moves up guards against losses far more fiercely than they chase equivalent gains — when the stakes are trivial, keeps three monitors for a portfolio that fits on one screen.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7f45371f-9ba9-454b-a136-ebbb8ee661aa', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.76},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.38,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.4,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one; leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. When the number turns red would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.62,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.71,"neuroticism":0.76}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Meme-coin rotator, steady in style: needs repeated reassurance that a decision was the right one; leaves loose ends and trusts future-self to handle them. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. When the number turns red would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b41edf75-05fa-411b-a5b0-ddeb7dc78e1d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.48,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.47,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.49,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"When cornered, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a steady prop-desk scalper who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and when no one is watching exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.58},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.65},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.58},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.52,"agreeableness":0.48,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'When cornered, discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened. Otherwise, a steady prop-desk scalper who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and when no one is watching exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
