('8782026e-aef9-4839-a880-b17cc83f5e90', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.88},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.31,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.49,"alpha":0.79,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. When there is no clean exit looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; in the small things, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.66},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.64},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.67}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.67,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.5,"agreeableness":0.51,"neuroticism":0.88}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced volatility arbitrageur who carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Finds one more piece of information to gather before acting. Collects half-finished manifestos and unconventional methods. When there is no clean exit looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; in the small things, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('1f4c3772-ced1-4501-b979-49a5196fa77c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.76},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.3},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.17,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Dividend-yield chaser, steady in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Trusts momentum over preparation. The instant the deadline moves up cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.66},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.73},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.68},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.8}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.77,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.83,"agreeableness":0.63,"neuroticism":0.76}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Dividend-yield chaser, steady in style: recharges by being around people, not away from them; reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Trusts momentum over preparation. The instant the deadline moves up cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.', 0.92, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2b56fb1f-4f10-4084-9bcb-68c787a1f3a8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.74},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.58,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.95,"alpha":0.8,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. This prop-desk scalper dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Once the exit narrows to one door cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — left to their own devices, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.65},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.79},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.71},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.74,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.81,"agreeableness":0.77,"neuroticism":0.74}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one. This prop-desk scalper dominates the room then wonders why others stayed quiet and rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Once the exit narrows to one door cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long — left to their own devices, backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9f05016c-4b96-4e94-8b67-b00ddf42ce95', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.43,"neuroticism":0.39},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.51,"narcissism":0.77,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.15,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. The moment risk appears, assumes the current streak is the new normal; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.76,"agreeableness":0.43,"neuroticism":0.39}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Algorithmic market-maker whose defining move is that they reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. The moment risk appears, assumes the current streak is the new normal; treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d31cbe49-9530-4465-9583-6726c79f8063', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.93},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.44,"narcissism":0.3,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.74,"alpha":0.74,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"A pronounced futures spreader who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Once the exit narrows to one door looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; as a rule, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.67},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.79},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.66}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.59,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.61,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.93}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'A pronounced futures spreader who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen. Prefers a slow loss to a fast, ownable mistake. Is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Once the exit narrows to one door looks away from bad news in the hope it resolves unwitnessed; as a rule, sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('5caa38fd-c664-4b41-90d4-a64f678a662e', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.38},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Under a deadline, overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs. Otherwise, a measured penny-stock gambler who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and left to their own devices trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.57},{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.52}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.38}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Under a deadline, overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs. Otherwise, a measured penny-stock gambler who defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely and treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and left to their own devices trusts the chart more than the fundamentals and won''t say why.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('34196c63-8c13-47b4-8042-66d49ef224e2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.76},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.39,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.31},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.45,"alpha":0.77,"beta":0.79},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This commodities speculator rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. The moment it stops being hypothetical feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly — day to day, screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.6},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.64},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.4,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.76}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Treats not-choosing as a safe choice right up until it is not. This commodities speculator rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and defaults to trust and gives the benefit of the doubt too freely. The moment it stops being hypothetical feels a loss twice as sharply as an equivalent gain and plans accordingly — day to day, screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bc730673-2d4f-4dde-b793-54bb90f5a957', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.74},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.42,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.76,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.8},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Pairs trader whose defining move is that they treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. In a pinch, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.72},{"slug":"sunk-cost","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.63,"conscientiousness":0.23,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.62,"neuroticism":0.74}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Pairs trader whose defining move is that they treats a plan as a suggestion the moment it is made. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them. Notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right. In a pinch, would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help; sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.9, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('9158a08e-bd69-4823-8a37-92a7178e6201', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.57},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.9,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.07,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"A pronounced value investor who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. The moment it stops being hypothetical takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; day to day, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.75},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.73}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.95,"conscientiousness":0.29,"extraversion":0.93,"agreeableness":0.3,"neuroticism":0.57}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced value investor who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Treats hesitation as the bigger risk. Treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. The moment it stops being hypothetical takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis; day to day, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
