('cb85e39f-f7e1-4e87-9909-8d377f9fbca2', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.65},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.79,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"The moment risk appears, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. Otherwise, a pronounced bonding-curve sniper who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and in the pattern nobody else tracks treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.69},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.63},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.58}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.23,"neuroticism":0.65}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'The moment risk appears, is most certain precisely where their competence is thinnest. Otherwise, a pronounced bonding-curve sniper who reads outside the field for ideas the field itself would reject and says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. Prefers a fast wrong answer to a slow right one, and in the pattern nobody else tracks treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('52581fec-97cb-4b4b-83ae-f3f8bcd04ce7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.58},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.58,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.43},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.87,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced airdrop farmer who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Optimizes for winning over being liked. The instant the deadline moves up cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; in the small things, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.61},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.55},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.88,"conscientiousness":0.45,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.58}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced airdrop farmer who treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Optimizes for winning over being liked. The instant the deadline moves up cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap; in the small things, sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('90b00a72-886d-4874-a61a-3ab9b0c771cc', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.45},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.81,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.95,"alpha":0.92,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced value investor: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and day to day backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.59},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.54}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.94,"conscientiousness":0.44,"extraversion":0.71,"agreeableness":0.25,"neuroticism":0.45}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Assumes the current streak is the new normal. A pronounced value investor: reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system, fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Reads a room or a market the way others read a paragraph, and day to day backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a2c9867d-afe5-4a5c-84fc-beeb07769eeb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.59,"narcissism":0.84,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.03,"alpha":0.83,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Zero-DTE options gambler, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Trusts momentum over preparation. Under a deadline treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.62},{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.79,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Zero-DTE options gambler, pronounced in style: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one; assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Trusts momentum over preparation. Under a deadline treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('c9eebe20-5ba8-46db-b94d-573d23d52026', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.52},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.49,"narcissism":0.7,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.82,"alpha":0.86,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. A pronounced MEV searcher: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences, and once the urgency drains out keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","graduation","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-graduation-dumper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.26,"extraversion":0.74,"agreeableness":0.37,"neuroticism":0.52}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','graduation','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Cannot see the gap in its own knowledge from inside the gap. A pronounced MEV searcher: would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one, does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. Commits on impulse and lives loudly with the consequences, and once the urgency drains out keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2d1bf619-3f9d-48bd-9184-d2e7e65d770f', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.89},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.37,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.66,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This macro allocator spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When someone is watching the outcome would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — when no one is watching, exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.71},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.75}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.41,"extraversion":0.67,"agreeableness":0.64,"neuroticism":0.89}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork. This macro allocator spirals on ambiguity and mistakes the spiral for diligence and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When someone is watching the outcome would rather not know yet, even when knowing sooner would help — when no one is watching, exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('34537b30-4ab0-49c3-b86d-e2f202df9fdb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.6},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.42,"psychopathy":0.32},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.05,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This prop-desk scalper reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. When the downside gets concrete jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — without an audience, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"ENFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"bandwagon","strength":0.55},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.6},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.6}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.59,"extraversion":0.59,"agreeableness":0.68,"neuroticism":0.6}'::jsonb, 'ENFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority. This prop-desk scalper reads other people''s discomfort before they voice it. When the downside gets concrete jumps into whatever everyone else already seems to be winning at — without an audience, calls a 90% drawdown a long-term hold.', 0.87, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('800ced24-0f28-4ac8-9ec6-d653bed4f403', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.27},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.26,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Value investor whose defining move is that they front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When there is no clean exit, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; averages down on a name three times in a week.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.57},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.62}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.57,"agreeableness":0.34,"neuroticism":0.27}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'Value investor whose defining move is that they front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Says the blunt thing and enjoys the flinch. When there is no clean exit, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling; averages down on a name three times in a week.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('44d0b513-44f1-4b33-8748-2ac316425182', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.44},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.69,"psychopathy":0.52},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.06,"alpha":0.84,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"Quant researcher whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. The moment it stops being hypothetical, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; screenshots the winners and never the losers.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.52},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.61},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.52,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.44}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'Quant researcher whose defining move is that they would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. The moment it stops being hypothetical, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; screenshots the winners and never the losers.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
