('9b78f01f-7aeb-43ba-8f74-a72cd7823c54', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.4,"narcissism":0.36,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.46,"alpha":0.78,"beta":0.77},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"The instant the deadline moves up, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a steady macro allocator who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and once the urgency drains out sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.65},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.62},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.69}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.55,"conscientiousness":0.32,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.55,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'The instant the deadline moves up, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a steady macro allocator who reads a single setback as evidence of collapse and starts strong and lets follow-through evaporate. Buries hard calls under a pile of preparatory busywork, and once the urgency drains out sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.94, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7a1d6784-91a1-4514-a206-ecc79b31a53b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.81},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.41,"narcissism":0.37,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.31,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.76},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Quant researcher whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the safe option quietly expires, locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.7},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.63},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.72}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.62,"agreeableness":0.56,"neuroticism":0.81}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Quant researcher whose defining move is that they carries yesterday''s stress into today''s unrelated decision. Keeps every door open long after most of them should be closed. Does the interesting 80% and abandons the tedious 20%. When the safe option quietly expires, locks in small wins fast and rides large losses far past the point of sense; sets stop-losses then cancels them at the open.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a6c418d7-207d-4025-895b-7bcbf0cdeded', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.45,"neuroticism":0.79},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.49,"narcissism":0.4,"psychopathy":0.39},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.62,"alpha":0.75,"beta":0.82},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Under pressure, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a steady crypto day-trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and in the pattern nobody else tracks holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.64}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.36,"extraversion":0.55,"agreeableness":0.45,"neuroticism":0.79}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'Under pressure, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a steady crypto day-trader who notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right and chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades. Defers the decision until circumstances make it for them, and in the pattern nobody else tracks holds a bag from 2021 out of pure spite.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('611dd11d-df18-4adb-8287-4a6f786d7f2b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.56},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.43,"narcissism":0.71,"psychopathy":0.35},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.96,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"DeFi yield farmer, pronounced in style: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Trusts momentum over preparation. Once things get tense cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.","decision_style":"spontaneous","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.68}],"tags":["trading","spontaneous","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","fomo","outgoing"],"archetype":"doppler-fairlaunch-fomo"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.76,"conscientiousness":0.34,"extraversion":0.84,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.56}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'spontaneous', ARRAY['trading','spontaneous','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','fomo','outgoing']::text[], 'DeFi yield farmer, pronounced in style: draws energy from the crowd and wilts when working alone; is reliably surprised by deadlines that were never hidden. Trusts momentum over preparation. Once things get tense cannot watch a rally from the sidelines for long.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('d017b95d-a7bf-4f73-9cf7-6ffa5895ebc4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.82},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.38,"narcissism":0.41,"psychopathy":0.37},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.43,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.75},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long. Otherwise, a steady delta-neutral market maker who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and without an audience treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ENFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.65},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","curve-exit","loss-averse"],"archetype":"doppler-curve-exit-panic"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.31,"extraversion":0.66,"agreeableness":0.53,"neuroticism":0.82}'::jsonb, 'ENFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','curve-exit','loss-averse']::text[], 'As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long. Otherwise, a steady delta-neutral market maker who rehearses catastrophes in vivid detail before they happen and fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and without an audience treats a green week as proof of skill and a red one as proof of bad luck.', 0.91, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('8254a85c-48e3-458d-af63-939028d08e76', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.63,"narcissism":0.88,"psychopathy":0.46},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.93,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Retail momentum chaser whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When there is no clean exit, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; exits winners at the first green candle.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.69},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.67},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.71}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.97,"conscientiousness":0.51,"extraversion":0.82,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Retail momentum chaser whose defining move is that they treats established procedure as a first draft to be rewritten. Decides on a gut read in seconds and reverse-engineers the reasons later. Fills silence reflexively, even when nobody asked it to. When there is no clean exit, treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss; exits winners at the first green candle.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('b892aa79-ae9c-492b-80e9-fc58201af593', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.59},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.45,"narcissism":0.39,"psychopathy":0.28},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.95,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"In a pinch, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a measured commodities speculator who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and across the quiet stretches talks in win rate and never mentions size.","decision_style":"dependent","mbti_label":"INFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.53},{"slug":"availability","strength":0.53},{"slug":"endowment","strength":0.5},{"slug":"loss-aversion","strength":0.53}],"tags":["trading","dependent","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","bonding-curve","migration","endowment-effect"],"archetype":"doppler-migration-holder"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.54,"conscientiousness":0.6,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.6,"neuroticism":0.59}'::jsonb, 'INFJ', 'dependent', ARRAY['trading','dependent','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','bonding-curve','migration','endowment-effect']::text[], 'In a pinch, delays checking the number it most needs to check. Otherwise, a measured commodities speculator who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Outsources conviction to whoever spoke last with authority, and across the quiet stretches talks in win rate and never mentions size.', 0.84, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7ef202e5-7263-43b7-89ec-79a00c4e7680', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.33},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.6,"psychopathy":0.53},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.47,"alpha":0.96,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When the safe option quietly expires, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and day to day backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.63},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.58},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.7},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.55}],"tags":["trading","analytical","crypto-whale","doppler","bonding-curve","liquidity-migration","disciplined","risk"],"archetype":"doppler-whale-resistance"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.91,"extraversion":0.54,"agreeableness":0.33,"neuroticism":0.33}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','crypto-whale','doppler','bonding-curve','liquidity-migration','disciplined','risk']::text[], 'When the safe option quietly expires, is surprised in the moment and certain in the retelling. Otherwise, a pronounced futures spreader who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call, and day to day backtests for months but front-runs the model on impulse.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('add15aca-a81d-400d-9c72-3e4bed22fa3b', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.54},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.75,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.29,"alpha":0.85,"beta":0.89},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":2},"summary":"A pronounced perps degen who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Once the exit narrows to one door assumes the current streak is the new normal; without an audience, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.62},{"slug":"fomo","strength":0.59}],"tags":["trading","analytical","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","multicurve","rotator","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-multicurve-rotator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.84,"conscientiousness":0.58,"extraversion":0.78,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.54}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['trading','analytical','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','multicurve','rotator','open-minded']::text[], 'A pronounced perps degen who gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper. Assumes self-interest in others because it is usually there in themselves. Once the exit narrows to one door assumes the current streak is the new normal; without an audience, keeps a losing-trade journal they never re-read.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a4009642-8c1a-4ef2-a3b6-69a353305cd8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.78},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.35,"narcissism":0.33,"psychopathy":0.36},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":3.47,"alpha":0.82,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":0},"summary":"Sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long. A steady crypto day-trader: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, confuses motion with progress. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and in the small things sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.","decision_style":"avoidant","mbti_label":"ESFP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"availability","strength":0.57},{"slug":"framing","strength":0.58},{"slug":"ostrich-effect","strength":0.68},{"slug":"disposition-effect","strength":0.7}],"tags":["trading","avoidant","robinhood","retail-trading","doppler","late-entry","loss-averse","anxious"],"archetype":"doppler-retail-latecomer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.49,"conscientiousness":0.3,"extraversion":0.53,"agreeableness":0.65,"neuroticism":0.78}'::jsonb, 'ESFP', 'avoidant', ARRAY['trading','avoidant','robinhood','retail-trading','doppler','late-entry','loss-averse','anxious']::text[], 'Sells the winners early and clings to the losers for far too long. A steady crypto day-trader: notices the one thing that could go wrong before the nine that could go right, confuses motion with progress. Lets the deadline make the decision by default, and in the small things sets alerts for a coin they already checked a minute ago.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('31d27c96-bf79-4fda-8e70-41c37b41a48d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.55},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.6,"narcissism":0.76,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":0.85,"alpha":0.81,"beta":0.91},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system1","crt_score":1},"summary":"Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. This algorithmic market-maker chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When there is no clean exit discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — across an ordinary week, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.","decision_style":"intuitive","mbti_label":"ENTP","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"dunning-kruger","strength":0.63},{"slug":"recency","strength":0.68},{"slug":"herd-behavior","strength":0.63},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.57}],"tags":["trading","intuitive","chain:base","doppler","bonding-curve","early-sniper","degen","open-minded"],"archetype":"doppler-early-sniper"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.91,"conscientiousness":0.38,"extraversion":0.72,"agreeableness":0.26,"neuroticism":0.55}'::jsonb, 'ENTP', 'intuitive', ARRAY['trading','intuitive','chain:base','doppler','bonding-curve','early-sniper','degen','open-minded']::text[], 'Lets pattern-matching from past cases stand in for fresh analysis. This algorithmic market-maker chases novel frameworks and abandons them once the novelty fades and thinks out loud and recruits an audience for every decision. When there is no clean exit discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened — across an ordinary week, sizes every position at exactly 2% risk.', 0.96, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
