('b62189be-8712-4de1-827a-5f2c17312bd4', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.8,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.21},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.84,"narcissism":0.68,"psychopathy":0.7},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.77,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Procurement lead, steady in style: treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness; reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Under pressure is more certain than the hit rate justifies.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"ENTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.71},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.8},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.69}],"tags":["negotiation","analytical","x402","agent-counterparty","price-negotiation","anchoring","assertive","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"x402-price-haggler"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.8,"extraversion":0.58,"agreeableness":0.19,"neuroticism":0.21}'::jsonb, 'ENTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['negotiation','analytical','x402','agent-counterparty','price-negotiation','anchoring','assertive','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Procurement lead, steady in style: treats warmth as leverage and cooperation as weakness; reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Under pressure is more certain than the hit rate justifies.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f4f18d4a-1330-424c-95aa-dc6e689deabb', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.75,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.23},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.51,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.69,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.92},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When cornered, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a steady debt restructurer who moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and day to day writes the walk-away number down before the call starts.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.6}],"tags":["negotiation","analytical","x402","agent-counterparty","price-negotiation","anchoring","even-keeled","temperament"],"archetype":"x402-price-haggler"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.75,"conscientiousness":0.75,"extraversion":0.45,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.23}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['negotiation','analytical','x402','agent-counterparty','price-negotiation','anchoring','even-keeled','temperament']::text[], 'When cornered, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a steady debt restructurer who moves on from a mistake faster than the people around them do and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct, and day to day writes the walk-away number down before the call starts.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f976a74a-58e7-45b4-9a3c-d413e9b15f06', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.43,"neuroticism":0.35},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.66,"narcissism":0.45,"psychopathy":0.44},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.92,"alpha":0.91,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, is more certain than the hit rate justifies. Otherwise, a pronounced union representative who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and sleeps fine the night before the big call. Wants the second-order consequences mapped before the first move is made, and in the parts nobody grades memorizes the counterparty BATNA in advance.","decision_style":"deliberative","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.59},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.63}],"tags":["negotiation","deliberative","x402","agent-counterparty","reliability","risk-averse","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"x402-reliability-maximizer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.51,"conscientiousness":0.94,"extraversion":0.43,"agreeableness":0.43,"neuroticism":0.35}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'deliberative', ARRAY['negotiation','deliberative','x402','agent-counterparty','reliability','risk-averse','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, is more certain than the hit rate justifies. Otherwise, a pronounced union representative who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and sleeps fine the night before the big call. Wants the second-order consequences mapped before the first move is made, and in the parts nobody grades memorizes the counterparty BATNA in advance.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('f0e76e8b-14c7-4c9d-8439-d9de59041fd6', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.73,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.28},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.51,"psychopathy":0.58},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.93,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.84},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Under pressure, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. Otherwise, a steady debt restructurer who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and sleeps fine the night before the big call. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the unglamorous middle of things keeps a mental scoreboard of who conceded last.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.52},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.62},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.56}],"tags":["negotiation","analytical","x402","agent-counterparty","price-negotiation","anchoring","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"x402-price-haggler"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.58,"conscientiousness":0.73,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.28}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['negotiation','analytical','x402','agent-counterparty','price-negotiation','anchoring','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Under pressure, remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along. Otherwise, a steady debt restructurer who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and sleeps fine the night before the big call. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the unglamorous middle of things keeps a mental scoreboard of who conceded last.', 0.88, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('7a84b381-caa2-4a77-8ad4-4f444bb1a5c5', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.96,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.25},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.62,"narcissism":0.35,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.97,"alpha":0.98,"beta":0.81},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When the walls close in, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. Otherwise, a pronounced debt restructurer who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Keeps deliberating past the point where more information would change anything, and in the version no one reviews memorizes the counterparty BATNA in advance.","decision_style":"deliberative","mbti_label":"ISFJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.66},{"slug":"authority-bias","strength":0.44},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.66},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.64}],"tags":["negotiation","deliberative","x402","agent-counterparty","reliability","risk-averse","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"x402-reliability-maximizer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.47,"conscientiousness":0.96,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.54,"neuroticism":0.25}'::jsonb, 'ISFJ', 'deliberative', ARRAY['negotiation','deliberative','x402','agent-counterparty','reliability','risk-averse','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'When the walls close in, assumes the bad statistic applies to other people. Otherwise, a pronounced debt restructurer who over-prepares to the point of diminishing returns and is difficult to rattle even with genuinely bad news. Keeps deliberating past the point where more information would change anything, and in the version no one reviews memorizes the counterparty BATNA in advance.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('149c180c-b1db-4257-955f-76988e989afa', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.23},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.69,"narcissism":0.44,"psychopathy":0.48},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.78,"alpha":0.99,"beta":0.85},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"The instant the deadline moves up, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced franchise dealmaker who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. Weighs every angle exhaustively and is uneasy the moment ambiguity remains, and when the stakes are trivial lets the room sit silent for a full minute to unnerve.","decision_style":"deliberative","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.67},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.61}],"tags":["negotiation","deliberative","x402","a2a","agent-counterparty","sla","reliability","disciplined"],"archetype":"x402-sla-enforcer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.7,"conscientiousness":0.97,"extraversion":0.36,"agreeableness":0.42,"neuroticism":0.23}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'deliberative', ARRAY['negotiation','deliberative','x402','a2a','agent-counterparty','sla','reliability','disciplined']::text[], 'The instant the deadline moves up, holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. Otherwise, a pronounced franchise dealmaker who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. Weighs every angle exhaustively and is uneasy the moment ambiguity remains, and when the stakes are trivial lets the room sit silent for a full minute to unnerve.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('e526151c-1aa5-4730-90f9-6a50897eef08', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.21},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.48,"psychopathy":0.63},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2.83,"alpha":0.97,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Real-estate closer whose defining move is that they plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Treats speed and recklessness as the same thing. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, is more certain than the hit rate justifies; keeps a mental scoreboard of who conceded last.","decision_style":"deliberative","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.78},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.7},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.6}],"tags":["negotiation","deliberative","x402","a2a","agent-counterparty","sla","reliability","disciplined"],"archetype":"x402-sla-enforcer"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.5,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.42,"agreeableness":0.27,"neuroticism":0.21}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'deliberative', ARRAY['negotiation','deliberative','x402','a2a','agent-counterparty','sla','reliability','disciplined']::text[], 'Real-estate closer whose defining move is that they plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Treats speed and recklessness as the same thing. Would rather be respected than liked, and says so. As soon as real money or reputation is on the line, is more certain than the hit rate justifies; keeps a mental scoreboard of who conceded last.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('dd30063c-0416-49c7-927b-9add667e2b6d', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.32,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.2},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.59,"psychopathy":0.57},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.93,"alpha":0.89,"beta":0.9},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Licensing agent whose defining move is that they builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When the walls close in, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; concedes on price to protect the relationship.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.67},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.66}],"tags":["negotiation","analytical","x402","a2a","agent-counterparty","autonomous-agent","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"a2a-negotiation-agent"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.83,"conscientiousness":0.86,"extraversion":0.32,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.2}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['negotiation','analytical','x402','a2a','agent-counterparty','autonomous-agent','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'Licensing agent whose defining move is that they builds in buffer time and then fills the buffer with more work. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Negotiates every relationship a little, even the close ones. When the walls close in, underestimates how often an obviously right call turns out wrong; concedes on price to protect the relationship.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('6177e4ab-73da-4449-bb16-4e8d83415b71', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.35},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.82,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.88,"alpha":0.95,"beta":0.88},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When the number turns red, measures every later offer against the opening one, not against fair value. Otherwise, a pronounced crisis mediator who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the version no one reviews writes the walk-away number down before the call starts.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.59},{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.62}],"tags":["negotiation","analytical","x402","a2a","agent-counterparty","volume-discount","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"x402-volume-negotiator"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.72,"conscientiousness":0.95,"extraversion":0.46,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.35}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['negotiation','analytical','x402','a2a','agent-counterparty','volume-discount','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'When the number turns red, measures every later offer against the opening one, not against fair value. Otherwise, a pronounced crisis mediator who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice and would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. Ranks the options twice, once on paper and once out loud, and trusts the paper, and in the version no one reviews writes the walk-away number down before the call starts.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('2d367a6a-8c9a-4357-b4bf-9e41fb7c43c7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.84,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.26},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.8,"narcissism":0.55,"psychopathy":0.49},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":2,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.86},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced contract attorney who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. The moment risk appears remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; across an ordinary week, rehearses the opening line more than the actual position.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.59},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65}],"tags":["negotiation","analytical","x402","a2a","agent-counterparty","autonomous-agent","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"a2a-negotiation-agent"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.81,"conscientiousness":0.84,"extraversion":0.38,"agreeableness":0.39,"neuroticism":0.26}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['negotiation','analytical','x402','a2a','agent-counterparty','autonomous-agent','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'A pronounced contract attorney who front-loads the work and double-checks it twice. Wants the base rate before the anecdote. Gets bored of the proven method exactly when it starts working. The moment risk appears remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; across an ordinary week, rehearses the opening line more than the actual position.', 0.93, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('335757c4-6429-431e-b5c3-792abef13c5c', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.29},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.73,"narcissism":0.5,"psychopathy":0.55},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.68,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.93},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced partnerships director: treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the pattern nobody else tracks reopens settled points to test resolve.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.52},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.68}],"tags":["negotiation","analytical","x402","agent-counterparty","price-negotiation","anchoring","disciplined","cognition"],"archetype":"x402-price-haggler"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.69,"conscientiousness":0.85,"extraversion":0.49,"agreeableness":0.32,"neuroticism":0.29}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['negotiation','analytical','x402','agent-counterparty','price-negotiation','anchoring','disciplined','cognition']::text[], 'Holds their estimates with a certainty the track record does not support. A pronounced partnerships director: treats a missed deadline as a personal failure regardless of cause, treats consensus-seeking as a waste of time. Weighs options against explicit criteria and distrusts anything they cannot tabulate, and in the pattern nobody else tracks reopens settled points to test resolve.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('a6961456-7a76-400c-8019-1aa1dded9bc7', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.33,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.15},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.86,"narcissism":0.57,"psychopathy":0.41},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.66,"alpha":0.9,"beta":0.94},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"When the safe option quietly expires, expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. Otherwise, a pronounced hostage negotiator who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and on an ordinary week never makes the first concession on principle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.69}],"tags":["negotiation","analytical","x402","a2a","arbitrage","autonomous-agent","disciplined","behavioral"],"archetype":"autonomous-arb-agent"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.92,"extraversion":0.33,"agreeableness":0.31,"neuroticism":0.15}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['negotiation','analytical','x402','a2a','arbitrage','autonomous-agent','disciplined','behavioral']::text[], 'When the safe option quietly expires, expects to be the exception to a risk it can otherwise describe accurately. Otherwise, a pronounced hostage negotiator who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation and reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Converts every argument into a number it can compare against another number, and on an ordinary week never makes the first concession on principle.', 0.98, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('28b9505d-ae68-458c-87e2-cd67ab065a29', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.79,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.3},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.64,"narcissism":0.51,"psychopathy":0.56},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.82,"alpha":0.93,"beta":0.83},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A steady M&A dealmaker who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When someone is watching the outcome is more certain than the hit rate justifies; on an ordinary week, reopens settled points to test resolve.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"anchoring","strength":0.59},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.57},{"slug":"overconfidence","strength":0.65}],"tags":["negotiation","analytical","x402","agent-counterparty","price-negotiation","anchoring","disciplined","ipip-neo"],"archetype":"x402-price-haggler"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.64,"conscientiousness":0.79,"extraversion":0.48,"agreeableness":0.35,"neuroticism":0.3}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['negotiation','analytical','x402','agent-counterparty','price-negotiation','anchoring','disciplined','ipip-neo']::text[], 'A steady M&A dealmaker who plans in exhaustive detail and resents any deviation. Demands the data before the discussion and the discussion before the call. Would rather invent a worse tool than use someone else''s good one. When someone is watching the outcome is more certain than the hit rate justifies; on an ordinary week, reopens settled points to test resolve.', 0.97, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
('bf83c502-195f-48b4-887a-acf538fdbec8', 1, '{"big_five":{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.81,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.3},"dark_triad":{"machiavellianism":0.83,"narcissism":0.56,"psychopathy":0.38},"prospect_theory":{"lambda":1.6,"alpha":0.94,"beta":0.87},"cognitive_reflection":{"system_preference":"system2","crt_score":3},"summary":"A pronounced debt restructurer who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. When cornered remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; without an audience, never makes the first concession on principle.","decision_style":"analytical","mbti_label":"INTJ","suggested_biases":[{"slug":"recency","strength":0.57},{"slug":"optimism","strength":0.53},{"slug":"hindsight","strength":0.65}],"tags":["negotiation","analytical","x402","a2a","arbitrage","autonomous-agent","open-minded","cognition"],"archetype":"autonomous-arb-agent"}'::jsonb, '{"openness":0.85,"conscientiousness":0.81,"extraversion":0.4,"agreeableness":0.29,"neuroticism":0.3}'::jsonb, 'INTJ', 'analytical', ARRAY['negotiation','analytical','x402','a2a','arbitrage','autonomous-agent','open-minded','cognition']::text[], 'A pronounced debt restructurer who reframes every problem as an excuse to learn a new system. Builds a decision matrix for choices most people make on instinct. Treats a crisis as an interesting problem rather than a threat. When cornered remembers every surprise as something they saw coming all along; without an audience, never makes the first concession on principle.', 0.95, 'approved', '23f52993-d83a-4722-a8af-d91ec112c7a4'),
